tepdaughter%2C%20according%20to%20the%20book.%20So%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20bought%20his%20father%20a%20yacht%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20Errol%20Musk%20live%20on%20it%20alone%20and%20only%20see%20his%20family%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tried%20threats%2C%20rewards%2C%20and%20arguments%20to%20change%20my%20father%20for%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Elon%20Musk%20told%20Isaacson%20in%20the%20book.%20%26quot%3BNo%20way%2C%20it%20just%20got%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20Elon%20Musk%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20ahead%20of%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%20returned%20to%20South%20Africa%20in%202003.%20He%20told%20Insider%20that%20when%20his%20family%20followed%20him%20back%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20they%20had%20to%20take%20extra%20steps%20to%20get%20into%20the%20country%20because%20his%20son%20had%20%26quot%3Btaken%20their%20passports.%26quot%3B%20The%20family%20had%20left%20the%20US%20without%20telling%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%2C%20Errol%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%20said%20he%20divorced%20Heide%20Bezuidenhout%20in%202004%2C%20which%20made%20Jana%20no%20longer%20his%20stepdaughter.%20He%20then%20fathered%20a%20child%20with%20Jana%20in%202017%2C%20when%20she%20was%20in%20her%2030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20lonely%2C%20lost%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20elder%20Musk%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fmusk-s-father-has-baby-with-stepdaughter-tndqvh3v6%5C%22%3EThe%20Sunday%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202018.%20%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20led%20to%20another%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20call%20it%20God's%20plan%20or%20nature's%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EErrol%20Musk%20and%20his%20former%20stepdaughter%20moved%20in%20together%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%20told%20Insider%20that%20Jana%C2%A0moved%20in%20with%20him%20in%202014.%20He%20was%20already%20living%20with%20his%2014-year-old%20daughter%20Rose%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20fathered%C2%A0with%20Heide.%20Errol%20said%20Jana%20showed%20up%20after%20a%20man%20she'd%20been%20living%20with%20had%20%26quot%3Bthrown%20her%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsaacson%20said%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Kimbal%20Musk%2C%20were%20%26quot%3Bcreeped%20out%20and%20furious%26quot%3B%20about%20Jana's%20pregnancy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20actually%20slowly%20making%20amends%20with%20my%20father%2C%26quot%3B%20Kimbal%20Musk%20told%20Isaacson%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20then%20he%20had%20a%20child%20with%20Jana%20and%20I%20said%2C%20'You're%20done%2C%20you're%20out.%20I%20never%20want%20to%20speak%20to%20you%20again.'%20And%20I%20haven't%20spoken%20to%20him%20since.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%20denied%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider%20that%20his%20son%20Kimbal%20was%20upset%20about%20the%20pregnancy.%20Kimbal%20Musk%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Elon%20Musk%20learned%20of%20his%20father's%20relationship%20with%20Jana%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Fculture%2Fculture-features%2Felon-musk-the-architect-of-tomorrow-120850%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20Rolling%20Stone%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202017%20that%20his%20father%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20terrible%20human%20being.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20biography%2C%20Isaacson%20said%20Elon%20Musk%20%E2%80%94%20who%20had%20been%20giving%20his%20father%20stipends%20of%20between%20%242%2C000%20to%20%245%2C000%20a%20month%20since%202010%20%E2%80%94%20temporarily%20stopped%20sending%20the%20funds%20when%20he%20learned%20his%20father%20had%20a%20child%20with%20his%20former%20stepdaughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bgrateful%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20funds%20and%20only%20had%20to%20ask%20Elon%20for%20financial%20support%20once%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%20later%20had%20another%20child%20with%20Jana%20in%202022%20and%20Elon%20Musk%20learned%20of%20the%20second%20pregnancy%20on