s%20of%20which%20visited%20the%20hostel%20and%20talked%20to%20the%20stakeholders%2C%20however%2C%20could%20not%20conclusively%20say%20in%20its%20report%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctragic%20fall%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20student%20which%20led%20to%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2013%20men%2C%20all%20former%20or%20current%20students%2C%20who%20were%20boarders%20of%20the%20hostel%2C%20were%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20it%20seems%2C%20he%20(the%20victim)%20was%20singled%20out%20for%20ragging%2C%20which%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20a%20systematic%20planned%20manner%2C%20having%20deliberately%20isolating%20him%20for%20severe%20ragging%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20batch-mates%20were%20far%20from%20him%20attending%20a%20hostel%20general%20body%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%20that%20the%20first-year%20undergraduate%20student%20of%20the%20Bengali%20department%20was%20ragged%20in%20phases%20on%20that%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20around%206.30%20pm%2C%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20room%20along%20with%206-7%20other%20freshers%20by%20one%20of%20the%20main%20accused%20where%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20shout%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20objectionable%2C%20sexist%2C%20and%20abusive%E2%80%9D%20words%20towards%20the%20female%20residents%20of%20the%20adjacent%20police%20quarters.%20After%20being%20compelled%20to%20follow%20the%20commands%2C%20he%20burst%20into%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20session%20of%20ragging%20took%20place%20in%20another%20room%2C%20between%209%20pm%20and%2010.45%20pm%2C%20where%20the%20boy%20was%20forced%20to%20put%20his%20signature%20in%20a%20complaint%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20Dean%20of%20Student%2C%20allegedly%20drafted%20by%20seniors%2C%20against%20a%20day%20scholar%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Bangla%2C%20in%20presence%20of%20nearly%2012-15%20boarders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20this...%2C%20the%20freshers%2C%20except%20the%20boy%2C%20were%20asked%20to%20attend%20an%20all%20hostellers%20General%20Body%20(GB)%20meeting%20which%20was%20held%20at%20the%20playground%20adjacent%20to%20A1%20block%20at%20around%2011%20pm%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20who%20deposed%20before%20the%20panel%20said%20while%20the%20GB%20meeting%20was%20on%2C%20the%20boy%20was%20seen%20standing%20in%20the%20lobby%20of%20the%20second%20floor%20along%20with%20two%20boarders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20deposed%20reported%20to%20the%20committee%20that%20there%20was%20a%20loud%20cry%20(for%20help)%20by%20someone%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20A-2%20block%20at%20past%2011.30%20pm.%20One%20of%20them%20who%20rushed%20to%20the%20spot%20after%20hearing%20the%20cry%20reported%20to%20have%20seen%20the%20boy%20running%20naked%2C%20and%20when%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20enter%20a%20room%2C%20two-three%20seniors%20pulled%20him%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20reportedly%20again%20started%20running%20desperately%20along%20the%20corridor%20of%20the%202nd%20floor%20A-2%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BInformation%20regarding%20the%20subsequent%20movements%2C%20just%20prior%20to%20his%20fatal%20fall%2C%20is%20rather%20uncertain%20and%20vague%2C%20as%20none%20of%20the%20witnesses%20gave%20a%20clear-cut%20description%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20could%20help%20in%20ascertaining%20the%20cause%20and%20sequence%20of%20the%20mishap.%E2%80%9D%20The%20committee%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20minor%20was%20%E2%80%9Cseverely%20abused%20sexually%20too%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20large%20number%20of%20them%20found%20the%20victim%20lying%20on%20the%20road%20adjacent%20to%20the%20A-2%20block%20in%20a%20naked%20condition%20in%20supine%20position.%20At%20that%20time%20the%20victim%20was%20found%20profusely%20bleeding%20from%20nostrils%2C%20ears%20and%20mouth%20and%20possibly%20from%20the%20back%20of%20the%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20covered%20the%20lower%20body%20part%20of%20the%20victim%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98gamchha'%20(traditional%20cotton%20towel%2C%20and%20took%20him%20to%20a%20hospital%20where%20he%20died.%20The%20report%20flagged%20the%20planned%20isolation%20and%20subsequent%20ragging%20of%20the%20boy%2C%20as%20being%20a%20well%20thought%20of%20act%20of%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695041160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Ff8uuq8cs_jadavpur-university-fb_625x300_09_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjadavpur-university-students-death-probe-panel-he-was-singled-out-for-ragging-4400857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20inquiry%20committee%20formed%20by%20Jadavpur%20University%20to%20probe%20into%20the%20circumstances%20leading%20to%20the%20death%20of%20a%20fresher%20has%20concluded%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20singled%20out%20for%20severe%20pre-planned%20ragging%2C%20which%20included%20possible%20sexual%20abuse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjadavpur-university-students-death-probe-panel-he-was-singled-out-for-ragging-4400857%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farida%20recalls%20Big%20B%20and%20Jaya's%20dating%20days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695040995000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103760556%2Cimgsize-55502.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffarida-jalal-talks-about-working-with-amitabh-bachchan-and-jaya-bachchan-recalls-the-time-when-the-iconic-couple-was-dating%2Farticleshow%2F103760556.cms%22%2C%22sum