munalism%20and%20journalism%20has%20been%20completely%20erased%2C%20how%20must%20the%20situation%20be%20countered%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20journalism%20becomes%20thoroughly%20communalised%2C%20is%20it%20entitled%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20journalism%E2%80%99s%20foundational%20principles%20and%20the%20safeguards%20provided%20to%20its%20practitioners%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20person%20who%20pulls%20the%20trigger%20becomes%20a%20news%20anchor%2C%20or%20a%20news%20anchor%20provokes%20others%20to%20pull%20the%20trigger%2C%20can%20these%20acts%20be%20justified%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20written%20and%20unwritten%20rules%20of%20journalism%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attempt%20in%20several%20quarters%20to%20brush%20off%20these%20questions%20and%20frame%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20of%2014%20prominent%20hate-spewing%20television%20anchors%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20journalism%20itself%2C%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20defence%20of%20communalism%20in%20the%20name%20of%20defending%20journalistic%20principles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20that%20matter%2C%20have%20television%20channel%20owners%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20their%20news%20anchors%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20allegations%20of%20hate%20speech%20made%20against%20them%20are%20completely%20false%2C%20and%20that%20their%20news%20anchors%20do%20not%20spread%20any%20kind%20of%20hate%20speech%20on%20air%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20more%20than%20the%20television%20network%20owners%2C%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20jumped%20to%20the%20news%20anchors%E2%80%99%20defence.%20Clearly%2C%20they%20are%20not%20defending%20ethical%20journalism%20but%20the%20hate%20speech%20which%20aids%20their%20politics.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20the%20ministers%20who%20have%20jumped%20into%20the%20fray%20are%20not%20exactly%20known%20for%20their%20stellar%20record%20in%20respecting%20journalistic%20principles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20could%20be%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20stance%20is%20prompted%20by%20a%20worry%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20move%20will%20succeed%20in%20turning%20the%20biggest%20front%20of%20communal%20politics%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20landscape%2C%20namely%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Egodi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(lap-dog)%20media%2C%20into%20a%20crucial%20political%20issue%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20of%20the%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association%20(NBDA)%20also%20criticised%20the%20boycott%20move%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20declaration%20of%20the%20list%20of%2014%20is%20tantamount%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbrowbeating%20journalists%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cstifling%20freedom%20of%20speech%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20is%20a%20throwback%20to%20the%20Emergency%20era.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20even%20the%20NBDA%20fought%20shy%20of%20saying%20that%20the%20anchors%20named%20in%20the%20list%20do%20not%20spread%20communal%20hatred%20on%20their%20shows%2C%20that%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20allegation%20is%20unfounded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20NBDA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnbdsa-news18-india-aman-chopra-fined%5C%22%3Ehad%20earlier%20imposed%20a%20fine%20on%20%3Cem%3ETV18%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20anchor%20Aman%20Chopra%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20two%20of%20his%20programmes.%20No%20wonder%20its%20statement%20has%20no%20mention%20of%20hate%20speech.%20Ironical%2C%20considering%20that%20the%20entire%20controversy%20is%20centred%20around%20the%20question%20of%20television%20news%20anchors%20giving%20vent%20to%20communal%20hatred%20on%20air.%20Why%20have%20the%20news%20channels%20and%20the%20NBDA%20not%20stated%20clearly%20that%20they%20will%20curb%20hate%20speech%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%5C%22%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%201926%20Call%20for%20Boycott%20of%20Newspapers%20Spreading%20Hatred%20Resonates%20With%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20Decision%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20journalism%20assumes%20the%20role%20of%20a%20flagbearer%20of%20communalism%2C%20can%20the%20resistance%20to%20it%20be%20anything%20but%20political%3F%20Moreover%2C%20without%20taking%20the%20issue%20to%20the%20people%2C%20would%20a%20stand%20against%20hate%20speech%20carry%20any%20meaning%3F%20Without%20engaging%20with%20these%20questions%2C%20debating%20whether%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20method%20of%20boycotting%20journalists%20is%20right%20or%20not%20is%20simply%20a%20waste%20of%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20listened%20carefully%20to%20the%20statements%20of%20Pawan%20Khera%20and%20Raghav%20Chaddha%2C%20spokespersons%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20They%20were%20not%20aggressive%20in%20any%20way%2C%20nor%20were%20they%20provoking%20their%20cadres%20to%20resort%20to%20aggression.%20In%20fact%2C%20Khera%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20did%20not%20hate%20the%20anchors%20named%20in%20the%20list%2C%20and%20in%20the%20event%20that%20the%20journalists%20realised%20the%20error%20of%20their%20ways%2C%20they%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20return%20to%20their%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20parties%20should%20appeal%20to%20their%20cadres%20and%20supporters%20to%20refrain%20from%20trolling%20the%2014%20journalists%20and%20threatening%20them%20with%20the%20prospect%20of%20imprisonment.%20This%20is%20a%20political%20battle%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20fought%20through%20democratic%20means%2C%20not%20in%20the%20way%20the%20BJP%20is%20known%20for.%20It%20is%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20prepare%20society%20to%20be%20politically%20aware.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20faced%20criticism%20of%20two%20kinds.%20On%20one%20side%20are%20the%20news%20anchors%2C%20their%20channels%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20who%20have%20termed%20the%20boycott%20an%20assault%20on%20democracy.%20The%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20on%20the%20same%20side%20is%20not%20without%20reason.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%20are%20those%20who%20consider%20the%20boycott%20valid%2C%20and%20a%20right%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20but%20add%20in%20the%20same%20breath%20that%20the%20alliance%20should%20not%20have%20publicised%20the%20names%20of%20the%20boycotted%20journalists.%20They%20see%20this%20move%20as%20a%20danger%20to%20journalism%2C%20little%20realising%20that%20there%20is%20no%20journalism%20left%20in%20those%20news%20channels.%20Journalists%20Sagarika%20Ghose%2C%20Vir%20Sanghvi%20and%20Rajdeep%20Sardesai%20are%20among%20those%20who%20subscribe%20to%20this%20view.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FbBNk4YLkECM%3Fsi%3DiXSF2c9LIJ-eOgAR%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20elaboration%20of%20the%20same%20view%2C%20journalist%20Shekhar%20Gupta%2C%20editor-in-chief%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThePrint%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20written%20that%20there%20have%20been%20instances%20of%20the%20BJP%20boycotting%20journalists%2C%20too%2C%20but%20they%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fnational-interest%2Fopposition-can-choose-to-boycott-tv-anchors-but-a-list-paints-a-target-on-journalists-backs%2F1764216%2F%5C%22%3Egone%20about%20it%20in%20a%20more%20%E2%80%9Csophisticated%E2%80%9D%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoes%20he%20really%20think%20that%20the%20way%20the%20media%20from%20the%20district%20level%20to%20Delhi%20has%20been%20stamped%20on%20from%20the%20time%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20can%20be%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98sophisticated%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20writes%20that%20but%20for%20one%20exception%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20never%20officially%20announced%20a%20boycott%20of%20journalists.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20ask%20what%20that%20exception%20was.%20Was%20it%20limited%20to%20not%20sending%20BJP%20spokespersons%20to%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20its%20pre-Adani%20avatar%3F%20Has%20Shekhar%20Gupta%20forgotten%20how%20journalists%20were%20singled%20out%20and%20marked%2C%20made%20to%20leave%20their%20jobs%2C%20among%20them%20female%20journalists%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20states%2C%20FIRs%20were%20filed%20against%20many%20journalists%20who%20were%20viciously%20trolled%20courtesy%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20IT%20cell.%20Were%20all%20these%20%E2%80%98sophisticated%E2%80%99%20methods%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnable%20to%20see%20the%20dangerous%20game%20of%20boycotting%20journalists%20that%20has%20been%20going%20on%20at%20various%20levels%20from%202014%20onwards%2C%20Shekhar%20Gupta%20has%20busied%20himself%20with%20crafting%20criticism%20against%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20boycott%20some%20news%20anchors.%20Has%20the%20dangerous%20game%20of%20boycotting%20journalists%20ceased%20during%20the%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20session%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW943NQli0ig%5C%22%3EBJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20had%20named%3C%2Fa%3E%20journalists%20Abhisar%20Sharma%20and%20Rohini%20Singh%20and%20levelled%20allegations%20against%20them.%20Was%20that%20a%20%E2%80%98sophisticated%E2%80%99%20move%20as%20well%3F%C2%A0%20Those%20remarks%20were%20first%20expunged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Flok-sabha-speaker-justifies-restoration-of-bjp-members-expunged-remarks-on-news-portal-2656741%5C%22%3Ebut%20later%20restored%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20very%20least%2C%20Shekhar%20Gupta%20should%20have%20mentioned%20that%20journalist%20Siddique%20Kappan%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20and%20two-year%20long%20incarceration%20in%20a%20jail%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20was%20not%20%E2%80%98sophisticated%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20allegations%20of%20money%20laundering%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20billions%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20have%20been%20digested%20by%20the%20dispensation%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98sophisticated%E2%80%99%20manner%3B%20and%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20is%20the%20example%20of%20Kappan%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20laundering%20Rs%205%2C000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fkaran-thapar-interview-sebi-former-chairman-damodaran-adani-financial-times%5C%22%3EFormer%20SEBI%20Chief%20Says%20Adani%20Story%20by%20FT-OCCRP%20%E2%80%98Very%20Persuasive%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20one%20more%20way%20of%20looking%20at%20the%20veteran%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20argument.%20If%20overwhelming%20pressure%20from%20the%20dispensation%20leads%20to%20the%20exit%20of%20an%20anchor%2C%20and%20all%20avenues%20of%20writing%20are%20closed%20off%20so%20that%20the%20journalist%20is%20unable%20to%20earn%20a%20living%20and%20sinks%20into%20oblivion%2C%20one%20should%20keep%20mum%2C%20for%20such%20things%20%E2%80%98keep%20happening%E2%80%99.%20Because%20this%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98sophisticated%E2%80%99%20way%20of%20getting%20things%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShekhar%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20entire%20word%20edifice%20rests%20on%20this%20foundation%20%E2%80%93%20such%20things%20keep%20happening.%20The%20only%20mode%20of%20boycott%20of%20journalists%20that%20he%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20is%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20of%2014%20anchors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20view%20that%20such%20instances%20keep%20happening%20turns%20a%20real%20danger%20into%20something%20superficial%2C%20normalising%20it%20in%20the%20process.%20My%20objection%20is%20to%20this%20very%20mode%20of%20normalisation%20%E2%80%93%20that%20such%20episodes%20have%20always%20occurred%20in%20journalism%20and%20are%20in%20fact%20occurring%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnyone%20can%20see%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20routine%20about%20the%20crisis%20of%20journalism%20that%20the%20Indian%20media%20is%20undergoing.%20But%20if%20the%20entire%20debate%20is%20cleverly%20framed%20in%20terms%20of%20an%20issue%20concerning%20journalism%2C%20it%20draws%20a%20veil%20over%20the%20real%20question%20of%20communalism%2C%20and%20the%20day%20is%20saved.%20The%20piece%20ends%20up%20normalising%20every%20means%20employed%20by%20this%20dispensation%20to%20repress%20journalism%20as%20a%20routine%20part%20of%20journalism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202016%2C%20when%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20suspended%20government%20advertising%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%20Patrika%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20its%20proprietor-editor%20Gulab%20Kothari%2C%20in%20a%20front-page%20editorial%2C%20described%20the%20move%20as%20dictatorial.%20Going%20by%20the%20logic%20of%20the%20argument%20that%20such%20instances%20keep%20happening%20in%20journalism%2C%20Kothari%20should%20not%20have%20questioned%20the%20then%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShekhar%20Gupta%20writes%20that%20it%20is%20a%20known%20fact%20that%20governments%20suspend%20advertisements%20to%20publications%20that%20are%20not%20%E2%80%9Csuitable%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20and%20I%20both%20know%E2%80%9D%20what%20that%20means.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20do%20we%20do%20anything%20with%20that%20knowledge%3F%20Is%20this%2C%20too%2C%20a%20sophisticated%20way%20of%20not%20raising%20such%20issues%20in%20decent%20and%20cultured%20circles%2C%20even%20though%20it%20may%20be%20a%20question%20of%20survival%20for%20the%20beleaguered%20publication%20or%20news%20channel%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20veteran%20journalist%20touches%20upon%20the%20issue%20of%20hate%20speech%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20hate%20sells%20and%20is%20so%20TRP%2Fmarket%20friendly%2C%20makes%20it%20worse.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-justice-joseph-nagarathna-hate-speech-religion%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98When%20Politics%20and%20Religion%20Are%20Segregated%2C%20This%E2%80%99ll%20Stop%E2%80%99%3A%208%20Quotes%20From%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Words%20on%20Hate%20Speech%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wonder%2C%20is%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20in%20such%20urgent%20need%20of%20some%2010-20%20crore%20rupees%20of%20revenue%20that%20a%20news%20anchor%20has%20to%20present%20a%20hate-filled%20debate%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%3F%20If%20that%20show%20were%20to%20be%20discontinued%2C%20would%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20be%20forced%20to%20auction%20off%20his%20palatial%20mansion%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20that%20should%20have%20been%20asked%20is%20whether%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20can%20cancel%20a%20hate-filled%20show%20on%20his%20television%20channel%20or%20not.%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20it%20is%20not%20Ambani%20who%20has%20the%20answer%20to%20this%20question%20but%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWho%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20that%20these%20debate%20shows%20are%20not%20an%20exercise%20in%20journalism%3B%20they%20are%20platforms%20to%20facilitate%20the%20expansion%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics.%20These%20aspects%20are%20completely%20missing%20in%20Shekhar%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20piece.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20employed%20language%20(English)%20to%20put%20a%20beautiful%20cloak%20of%20acceptability%2C%20or%20legitimacy%2C%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20communalism%2C%20as%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20some%20problem%20that%20journalism%20is%20facing.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20this%20article%20is%20a%20classic%20defence%20of%20communalism%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20journalism%2C%20one%20that%20should%20be%20mandatory%20reading%20in%20classrooms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJournalist%20Ajit%20Anjum%20has%20written%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20stopped%20sending%20its%20spokesperson%20to%20%3Cem%3EABP%3C%2Fem%3E%20anchor%20Sandeep%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20show.%20However%2C%20this%20case%20is%20very%20different%20from%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20boycott.%20Unlike%20the%20list%20of%2014%2C%20Chaudhary%20does%20not%20present%20shows%20that%20seek%20to%20foment%20communal%20hatred.%20He%20asks%20the%20questions%20that%20a%20journalist%20needs%20to%20ask.%20Yet%20the%20BJP%20has%20boycotted%20his%20show.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHas%20there%20been%20any%20statement%20either%20from%20the%20channels%20that%20have%20questioned%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20or%20the%20NBDA%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20of%20Sandeep%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20show%20is%20taking%20India%20dangerously%20close%20to%20an%20Emergency-like%20situation%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHas%20there%20been%20any%20statement%20either%20from%20the%20channels%20that%20have%20questioned%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20or%20the%20NBDA%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20of%20Sandeep%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20show%20is%20taking%20India%20dangerously%20close%20to%20an%20Emergency-like%20situation%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20their%20resolve%20to%20continue%20asking%20questions%2C%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20if%20one%20of%20them%20could%20post%20the%20link%20of%20a%20video%20to%20show%20how%20they%20ask%20questions%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20home%20minister%20of%20our%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20point%20is%20that%20everyone%20knows%20about%20the%20banishment%20of%20questions%20from%202014%20onwards.%20When%20one%20Union%20minister%20reminded%20the%20news%20anchor%20about%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20in%20prison%2C%20was%20that%20not%20intimidation%20by%20the%20minister%2C%20and%20an%20assault%20on%20democracy%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fundamental%20question%20is%20whether%20a%20political%20party%20should%20send%20its%20representative%20to%20shows%20that%20deepen%20communal%20polarisation.%20If%20the%20answer%20is%20no%2C%20then%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20political%20party%20should%20go%20through%20with%20its%20decision%20in%20an%20unstated%20manner.%20However%2C%20as%20a%20mode%20of%20democratic%20resistance%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20better%20than%20non-cooperation%2C%20or%20boycott%2C%20carried%20out%20in%20a%20public%20and%20transparent%20manner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20making%20its%20decision%20public%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20fight%20against%20communalism%20also%20necessitates%20taking%20a%20stand%20against%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egodi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(lap-dog)%20media%E2%80%99s%20journalism%20that%20has%20become%20thoroughly%20communalised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20not%20boycotting%20the%20named%20anchors%20because%20of%20their%20tough%20questions%2C%20the%20way%20Modi%20did%20many%20years%20ago%20when%2C%20offended%20by%20show%20host%20Karan%20Thapar%E2%80%99s%20questions%2C%20he%20simply%20took%20off%20the%20mic%20and%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20studio.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F0JeDveah7KQ%3Fsi%3DJefhQ-Cqf-T-lel7%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20earlier%20occasions%2C%20opposition%20parties%20have%20silently%20boycotted%20shows%20that%20sought%20to%20heighten%20the%20pitch%20of%20communal%20polarisation%2C%20as%20Shekhar%20Gupta%20has%20indicated%2C%20but%20it%20proved%20ineffective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20public%20decision%20to%20boycott%20anchors%20is%20not%20a%20knee-jerk%20response.%20It%20has%20come%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20watching%20such%20vitiated%20programmes.%20Courts%20too%20have%20asked%20if%20any%20anchor%20fomenting%20communal%20hatred%20has%20been%20taken%20off%20air.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20Supreme%20Court%20comments%20against%20hate%20speech%2C%20but%20despite%20court%20directives%2C%20have%20any%20channels%20been%20proceeded%20against%20on%20these%20grounds%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20disastrous%20consequences%20of%20hate-mongering%20shows%20are%20there%20for%20all%20to%20see.%20Wherever%20communal%20violence%20erupts%2C%20the%20government%20shuts%20down%20the%20internet.%20But%20the%20channels%20that%20broadcast%20programmes%20fomenting%20hate%20are%20never%20shut%20down.%20The%20quarters%20from%20where%20the%20communal%20project%20of%20godi%20journalism%20is%20getting%20its%20support%20is%20absolutely%20clear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fight%20against%20communalism%20cannot%20be%20fought%20secretively.%20Nor%20can%20there%20be%20a%20different%20set%20of%20rules%20for%20resisting%20communal%20hatred%20in%20different%20walks%20of%20life%20and%20from%20different%20platforms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20current%20context%2C%20all%20those%20who%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20resistance%20need%20to%20answer%20one%20question%20%E2%80%93%20the%20question%20I%20posed%20at%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20this%20piece%3A%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egodi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20media%20presents%20the%20biggest%20front%20of%20communalism%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20the%20act%20of%20taking%20a%20stand%20against%20communalism%20an%20act%20of%20opposing%20journalism%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Hindi%20original%20by%20Chitra%20Padmanabhan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fravish-kumar%5C%22%3ERavish%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%20You%20can%20find%20him%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40ravishkumar.official%5C%22%3E%40ravishkumar.official%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695040137000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F13095447%2FIMG_0163.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhen-journalism-becomes-the-flagbearer-of-hate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20attempt%20in%20some%20quarters%20to%20brush%20off%20these%20questions%20and%20frame%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20of%2014%20prominent%20hate-spewing%20TV%20anchors%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20journalism%20itself%2C%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20defence%20of%20communalism%20in%20the%20name%20of%20defending%20journalistic%20principles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhen-journalism-becomes-the-flagbearer-of-hate%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ramaswamy%20wants%20to%20'gut'%20H-1Bs%3A%20Good%20or%20bad%20for%20Indian%20techies%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695040116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103760097%2Cimgsize-20786.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.co