content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22479%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%20526w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%20247w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22583%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20word%20spread%20that%20the%20India%20Club%20was%20closing%20for%20good%20after%2070%20years%2C%20it%20caused%20more%20shock%20and%20sadness%20than%20if%20the%20Rolling%20Stones%20had%20split%20up.%20The%20queues%20have%20stretched%20all%20the%20way%20down%20the%20narrow%20flights%20of%20stairs%3B%20the%20bar%20could%20barely%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20demand%20for%20Cobras%20and%20Kingfishers%3B%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20personal%20look%20of%20a%20place%20which%20bore%20so%20many%20memories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20first%20went%20to%20the%20India%20Club%20more%20than%2040%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20started%20working%20across%20the%20road%20at%20Bush%20House%2C%20then%20the%20home%20of%20the%20BBC%20World%20Service.%20It%20was%20an%20oasis%20of%20calm%20amid%20the%20clamour%20of%20the%20city.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20point%20of%20connection%20with%20a%20sepia-tinged%20world%20of%20Indian%20nationalist%20students%20and%20the%20optimism%20of%20the%20independence%20era.%20The%20dated%20d%C3%A9cor%2C%20the%20modest%20prices%2C%20the%20portrait%20photo%20of%20former%20defence%20minister%20of%20India%20V.K.%20Krishna%20Menon%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20all%20spoke%20of%20the%20history%20of%20the%20institution%20and%20its%20importance%20as%20a%20link%20between%20India%20and%20those%20Brits%20who%20wished%20the%20nation%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThanks%20to%20the%20Marker%20family%2C%20who%20have%20run%20the%20club%20for%20almost%20thirty%20years%2C%20it%20has%20continued%20to%20flourish.%C2%A0%20The%20food%20was%20better%20than%20ever%2C%20the%20restaurant%20was%20always%20busy%20and%20the%20bar%20too%20was%20in%20demand.%20The%20India%20Club%20was%20not%20a%20failing%20institution.%20But%20the%20property%20is%20owned%20by%20a%20company%20intent%20on%20disembowelling%20the%20building%20and%20making%20it%20deliver%20a%20bigger%20financial%20return.%20So%20out%20with%20the%20past%3B%20in%20with%20the%20profit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20India%20Club%20shut%20down%20permanently%20on%20Sunday%20(September%2017).%20A%20sad%20day.%20Many%20of%20its%20customers%20regard%20this%20as%20an%20act%20of%20cultural%20vandalism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98To%20me%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20personal%20connection%E2%80%99%2C%20says%20Londoner%20Smita%20Tharoor.%20%E2%80%98My%20father%20was%20one%20of%20the%20founder%20members%20in%201951.%20It%E2%80%99s%20my%20dad%E2%80%99s%20history%20that%E2%80%99s%20disappearing%20forever%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20painful.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20340px)%2085vw%2C%20340px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18165623%2FPHOTO-2023-09-14-21-53-23-768x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22340%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18165623%2FPHOTO-2023-09-14-21-53-23-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18165623%2FPHOTO-2023-09-14-21-53-23-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18165623%2FPHOTO-2023-09-14-21-53-23.jpg%20900w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673517%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22454%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20India%20Club.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandran%20Tharoor%20was%20a%20newspaper%20man%20who%20spent%20much%20of%20the%201950s%20based%20in%20London.%20When%20he%20returned%20to%20London%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20popped%20in%20to%20the%20India%20Club%20for%20a%20curry%2C%20he%20commented%3A%20%E2%80%98it%20looks%20exactly%20like%20when%20I%20left%20in%20%E2%80%9958!%E2%80%99%20There%20was%20a%20timeless%20quality%20about%20the%20place.%20That%20was%20part%20of%20its%20charm.%20Smita%20Tharoor%2C%20who%20hosts%20the%20%E2%80%98Stories%20Seldom%20Told%E2%80%99%20podcast%2C%20had%20a%20last%20supper%20in%20the%20club%20in%20the%20past%20week.%20So%20have%20hundreds%20of%20other%20moist-eyed%20well-wishers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98The%20closure%20of%20the%20India%20Club%20is%20a%20sad%20reflection%20on%20the%20victory%20of%20capital%20over%20heritage%E2%80%99%2C%20says%20William%20Gould%2C%20professor%20of%20Indian%20History%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Leeds.%20%E2%80%98The%20club%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20sites%20for%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20largest%20diaspora%20from%20South%20Asia.%C2%A0%20It%20was%20a%20home%20away%20from%20home%20for%20new%20arrivals%20to%20the%20city%20for%20around%2070%20years%2C%20and%20hosted%20many%20of%20the%20communities%E2%80%99%20cultural%2C%20artistic%2C%20political%20and%20social%20events.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Gould%20prepared%20a%20report%20about%20the%20history%20of%20the%20building%20and%20the%20club%20to%20make%20the%20case%20that%20it%20should%20be%20regarded%20as%20a%20historically%20important%20site%20and%20protected%20from%20redevelopment.%20The%20building%20which%20houses%20the%20club%20was%20earlier%20the%20office%20of%20the%20India%20League%2C%20the%20exceptionally%20effective%20pro-independence%20lobby%20group%20led%20by%20Krishna%20Menon.%20It%20was%20where%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20case%20was%20developed%20and%20promulgated%20in%20the%20imperial%20capital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20India%20League%20helped%20establish%20the%20India%20Club%2C%20which%20counted%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Edwina%20Mountbatten%20among%20its%20founder%20members.%20The%20proximity%20of%20King%E2%80%99s%20College%2C%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%20and%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20provided%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20keen%2C%20if%20impecunious%2C%20customers.%20From%20its%20inception%2C%20it%20has%20also%20been%20a%20hang-out%20for%20Indian%20journalists%20based%20in%20London.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20its%20clientele%20changed%20from%20being%20mainly%20Indian%20to%20principally%20white%20British%2C%20but%20it%20retained%20an%20eclectic%20mix%20of%20habitues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20club%20was%20initially%20based%20nearby%20and%20moved%20to%20its%20enduring%20home%2C%20143%20The%20Strand%2C%20in%20the%20mid-1950s.%20The%20building%20is%20well%20over%20a%20100%20years%20old%2C%20and%20still%20has%20much%20of%20its%20original%20stained%20glass%2C%20tiles%20and%20fittings.%20Eating%20there%20really%20was%20like%20travelling%20back%20into%20another%20era.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18165648%2FIMG_8468-e1695037331167-225x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18165648%2FIMG_8468-e1695037331167-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18165648%2FIMG_8468-e1695037331167-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18165648%2FIMG_8468-e1695037331167.jpg%20900w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673518%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EEntrance%20to%20the%20India%20Club.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPart%20of%20the%20magic%20of%20the%20India%20Club%20was%20that%20it%20was%20a%20shared%20secret.%20It%20got%20hardly%20any%20passing%20trade.%20There%20was%20a%20door%20marked%20Hotel%20Strand%20Continental%2C%20and%20sometimes%20a%20board%20advertising%20Indian%20food%2C%20leading%20into%20a%20staircase%20so%20dark%20and%20serpentine%20as%20to%20repel%20all%20but%20the%20most%20intrepid.%20But%20the%20adventurous%20got%20their%20reward.%20The%20bar%2C%20cosy%20and%20(usually)%20genteel%2C%20was%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%20You%20had%20to%20trudge%20up%20another%20echoing%20flight%20of%20stairs%20to%20reach%20the%20restaurant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOlder%20customers%20can%20remember%20the%20shudder%20of%20disapproval%20in%20earlier%20days%20when%20you%20sought%20to%20order%20a%20beer%20in%20the%20restaurant.%20You%20were%20sent%20downstairs%20to%20the%20bar%20to%20carry%20up%20your%20own%20bottles.%20Others%20recall%20the%20legendary%20Doris%2C%20a%20formidable%20bar%20lady%20who%20took%20it%20upon%20herself%20to%20decide%20how%20much%20her%20customers%20should%20drink.%20As%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiaclub.co.uk%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Club%E2%80%99s%20own%20website%20proclaims%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20was%20always%20%E2%80%98charmingly%20eccentric%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20that%20charm%20has%20been%20lost%20and%20a%20cultural%20connection%20ruptured.%20The%20club%20is%20looking%20for%20alternative%20space%20nearby%2C%20but%20even%20if%20it%20succeeds%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20institution%20cannot%20easily%20be%20conjured%20up%20in%20a%20new%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20in%20the%20closing%20days%20of%20the%20club%2C%20the%20mood%20among%20diners%20and%20drinkers%20was%20irrepressibly%20upbeat.%20