ople%20to%20be%20skilled%20on%20AI%20enough%20that%20they%20can%20have%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20client%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0whether%20or%20not%20you're%20an%20associate%20or%20an%20experienced%20partner%20%E2%80%94%20so%20that%20you%20can%20identify%20opportunities%20for%20us%20to%20be%20able%20to%20go%20in%20and%20support%20that%20client%20and%20that%20AI%20transformation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20be%20able%20to%20support%20the%20firm%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Shannon%20Schuyler%2C%20US%20chief%20purpose%20and%20inclusion%20officer%20at%20PwC%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20is%20designed%20to%20teach%20partners%20and%20employees%20what%20AI%20is%20and%20how%20they%20can%20safely%20incorporate%20it%20into%20their%20work.%20After%20the%20initial%20round%20is%20complete%2C%20PwC%20plans%20to%20provide%20personalized%20training%20for%20certain%20teams%20and%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPwC's%20strategy%20to%20roll%20out%20monthly%20lessons%20for%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20employees%20points%20to%20what%20a%20big%20deal%20many%20business%20leaders%20expect%20AI%20and%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20generative%20AI%20will%20prove%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20despite%20the%20interest%20in%20GenAI%2C%20it's%20so%20new%20that%20there's%20not%20always%20enough%20expertise%20to%20go%20around.%20That's%20sending%20big%20companies%2C%20including%20the%20consulting%20giants%2C%20into%20a%20race%20to%20acquire%20expertise%20in%20AI%20and%20to%20train%20up%20their%20workforces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20PwC%2C%20that%20means%20educating%20everyone%20from%20longtime%20employees%20to%20new%20hires%20who%20might%20be%20recent%20graduates.%20The%20effort%20is%20part%20of%20a%20plan%20announced%20in%20April%20to%20invest%20%241%20billion%20over%20three%20years%20to%20expand%20the%20company's%20AI%20offerings%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20GenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEven%20some%20recent%20grads%20aren't%20tech%20savvy%20enough%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPwC's%20AI%20push%20comes%20as%20some%20of%20its%20entry-level%20hires%20don't%20always%20possess%20all%20of%20the%20technical%20chops%20they%20need%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20not%20just%20around%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20seen%20the%20type%20of%20digital%20acumen%20that%20we%20would%20like%20from%20the%20individuals%20coming%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Schuyler%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20workers'%20skill%20levels%20vary%20and%20that%20some%20have%20strong%20technical%20knowledge.%20To%20help%20ensure%20workers%20have%20the%20necessary%20skills%2C%20the%20company%20puts%20new%20hires%20and%20even%20interns%20through%20training%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchuyler%20said%20even%20some%20new%20hires%20with%20accounting%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20computer%20science%20degrees%20%E2%80%94%20people%20who%20have%20strong%20digital%20backgrounds%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0often%20aren't%20as%20experienced%20with%2C%20for%20example%2C%20some%20of%20the%20data-analytics%20software%20PwC%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20hires%20tend%20to%20be%20well%20versed%20in%20areas%20like%20search%2C%20but%20less%20so%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20tools%20like%20spreadsheets%2C%20Schuyler%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20use%20different%20types%20of%20applications%20that%20are%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20challenge%20for%20a%20company%20like%20PwC%20that%20tends%20to%20scoop%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20recent%20grads%20is%20that%20technology%20like%20GenAI%20is%20so%20new%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0at%20least%20in%20how%20it's%20being%20used%20to%20power%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20%E2%80%94%20that%C2%A0many%20universities%20are%20still%20working%20to%20incorporate%20GenAI%20into%20what%20they%20teach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20yet%20woven%20in%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0with%20any%20kind%20of%20sophistication%20%E2%80%94%20into%20the%20classes%20where%20we've%20seen%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Schuyler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20l