A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1004-stuart-binny-playerprofile%5C%22%3EStuart%20Binny%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Siraj's%20fiery%20spell%20consisted%20one%20over%20in%20which%20he%20scalped%20four%20wickets%20-%20the%20first%20time%20an%20Indian%20has%20done%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20fourth%20over%20of%20the%20match%20as%20Siraj%2C%20bowling%20his%20second%20over%2C%20broke%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20batting%20by%20scalping%20%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pathum%20Nissanka%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112358-pathum-nissanka-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPathum%20Nissanka%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sadeera%20Samarawickrama%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Charith%20Asalanka%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110487-charith-asalanka-playerprofile%5C%22%3ECharith%20Asalanka%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dhananjaya%20de%20Silva%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F50705-dhananjaya-maduranga-de-silva-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDhananjaya%20de%20Silva%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20over%20reduced%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%2012%2F5%20in%20four%20overs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sri%20Lankan%20team%20was%20in%20shock%20as%20were%20the%20fans%20present%20at%20the%20R%20Premadasa%20Stadium.%20One%20such%20reaction%20of%20a%20fan%20has%20gone%20viral.%20'X'%20handle%20%40GemsOfCricket%20posted%20the%20image%20and%20it%20got%20over%201%20lakh%2024%20thousand%20views.%20The%20image%20is%20a%20screengrab%20from%20Sunday's%20Asia%20Cup%20final%20after%20the%20fourth%20over%20with%20the%20scoreboard%20showing%2012%2F5.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIg2IfWtwSK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIg2IfWtwSK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Out%20Of%20Context%20Cricket%20(%40GemsOfCricket)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGemsOfCricket%2Fstatus%2F1703358876618485980%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20speedster%20Mohammed%20Siraj's%20fiery%20spell%20decimated%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20opening%20duo%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20scored%20a%20flawless%20fifty-run%20partnership%20as%20India%20won%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20for%20the%20eighth%20time.%20Leading%20India's%20fast%20bowling%20attack%2C%20Siraj%20ran%20through%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20top-order%20in%20a%20dazzling%20performance%20in%20the%20summit%20clash%20at%20the%20R%20Premadasa%20Stadium%20in%20Colombo%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20little%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20for%20India%20to%20lift%20the%20trophy%20in%20style.%20Sri%20Lanka%20fans%20were%20stunned%20into%20silence%20by%20their%20team's%20performance.%20The%20Men%20in%20Blue%20lifted%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20trophy%20after%20five%20years.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiraj%20had%20a%20dream%20spell%20as%20the%20entire%20Sri%20Lanka%20team%20was%20back%20in%20pavilion%20in%2015.2%20overs%20for%2050%20runs.%20%C2%A0Siraj%20took%20six%20wickets%20in%20seven%20overs%2C%20his%20best%20performance%20in%20ODIs.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeeding%20just%2051%20runs%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20made%20no%20mistakes%20and%20started%20with%20back-to-back%20boundaries%20off%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Matheesha%20Pathirana%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112669-matheesha-pathirana-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMatheesha%20Pathirana%3C%2Fa%3E's%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20over%20of%20the%20game%2C%20Gil