ished%22%3A1695035203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103757505%2Cimgsize-42496.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fvirat-kohli-reveals-what-fuels-team-indias-determination-to-win-world-cup%2Farticleshow%2F103757471.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Celebrated%20Virat%20Kohli%20says%20he%20and%20his%20teammates%20are%20ready%20to%20give%20their%20best%20in%20the%20upcoming%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20to%20make%20the%20dreams%20of%20Indian%20fans%20come%20true%20once%20again.%20The%20Men%20in%20Blue%20won%20the%20World%20Cup%20twice%2C%20with%20their%20last%20success%20coming%20in%202011%20when%20the%20competition%20was%20jointly%20hosted%20by%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fvirat-kohli-reveals-what-fuels-team-indias-determination-to-win-world-cup%2Farticleshow%2F103757471.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wilful%20Denial%20Of%20Sexual%20Relationship%20By%20Spouse%20Cruelty%3A%20Delhi%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWilful%20denial%20of%20sexual%20relationship%20by%20a%20spouse%20amounts%20to%20cruelty%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20ruled%20while%20upholding%20the%20divorce%20granted%20to%20a%20couple%20whose%20marriage%20effectively%20subsisted%20for%20barely%2035%20days%20and%20failed%20on%20account%20of%20non-consummation%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%2C%20while%20rejecting%20the%20wife's%20appeal%20against%20the%20family%20court%20order%20granting%20divorce%2C%20said%20the%20high%20court%20has%20ruled%20in%20a%20case%20that%20%26quot%3Bmarriage%20without%20sex%20is%20an%20anathema%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20nothing%20(more)%20fatal%20to%20marriage%20than%20disappointment%20in%20sexual%20relationship%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20court%20observed%2C%20the%20marriage%20was%20not%20consummated%20on%20account%20of%20resistance%20by%20the%20wife%20who%20also%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20claiming%20she%20was%20harassed%20for%20dowry%20about%20which%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20cogent%20evidence%26quot%3B.%20This%20can%20also%20be%20termed%20as%20cruelty%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20(a%20case)%2C%20it%20(the%20high%20court%20has)%20..%20observed%20that%20wilful%20denial%20of%20sexual%20relationship%20by%20a%20spouse%20amounts%20to%20cruelty%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20parties%20are%20newly%20married%20and%20this%20itself%20is%20a%20ground%20for%20grant%20of%20divorce%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20Neena%20Bansal%20Krishna%2C%20in%20an%20order%20dated%20September%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20present%20case%2C%20not%20only%20did%20the%20marriage%20between%20the%20parties%20subsist%20for%20barely%2035%20days%20but%20failed%20completely%20on%20account%20of%20deprivation%20of%20conjugal%20rights%20and%20non-consummation%20of%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20referring%20to%20the%20period%20the%20woman%20spent%20at%20her%20matrimonial%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20cannot%20be%20overlooked%20that%20such%20deprivation%20over%20a%20period%20of%20more%20than%2018%20years%20itself%20amounts%20to%20mental%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20recorded%20the%20couple%20got%20married%20according%20to%20Hindu%20customs%20and%20rites%20in%202004%20and%20the%20wife%20soon%20went%20back%20to%20her%20parental%20home%20and%20did%20not%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20husband%20later%20approached%20the%20family%20court%20for%20divorce%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20cruelty%20and%20desertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20family%20court%20%26quot%3Brightly%20concluded%26quot%3B%20that%20although%20the%20ground%20of%20desertion%20was%20not%20proved%2C%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20wife%20towards%20the%20husband%20amounted%20to%20cruelty%2C%20entitling%20him%20to%20the%20decree%20of%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaking%20allegations%20of%20dowry%20harassment%20resulted%20in%20registration%20of%20a%20FIR%20and%20the%20trial%20to%20follow%20can%20only%20be%20termed%20as%20an%20act%20of%20cruelty%20when%20the%20appellant%20has%20failed%20to%20prove%20even%20one%20incident%20of%20dowry%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20(a%20case)%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20laid%20down%20various%20acts%20which%20may%20amount%20to%20mental%20cruelty%20and%20one%20such%20illustration%20was%20unilateral%20decision%20of%20refusal%20to%20have%20intercourse%20for%20considerable%20period%20of%20time%20without%20there%20being%20no%20physical%20incapacity%20or%20valid%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20evidence%20on%20record%20established%20that%20the%20wife%20did%20not%20permit%20the%20husband%20to%20consummate%20the%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695034500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fcourt-generic_625x300_1527245477936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-wilful-denial-of-sexual-relationship-by-spouse-cruelty-4400674%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wilful%20denial%20of%20sexual%20relationship%20by%20a%20spouse%20amounts%20to%20cruelty%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20ruled%20while%20upholding%20the%20divorce%20granted%20to%20a%20couple%20whose%20marriage%20effectively%20subsisted%20for%20barely%2035%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%