-loss-why-investing-on-margin-is-risky.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNBC%20Make%20It%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20techie%2C%20living%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California%20started%20investing%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20parents%20before%20he%20was%20a%20teenager.%20His%20investment%20portfolio%20includes%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20crore%20in%20retirement%20and%20brokerage%20accounts%2C%20plus%20two%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20techie%20shared%20that%20he%20lost%20Rs%2067%20lakh%20in%20crypto%20between%20November%202021%20and%20June%202022.%20He%20told%20the%20media%20outlet%20that%20his%20losses%20include%20Rs%2024%20lakh%20of%20his%20original%20investment%20and%20an%20estimated%20Rs%2041%20lakh%20in%20unrealised%20gains.%20He%20told%20the%20publication%20that%20he%20had%20already%20invested%20around%20Rs%2033%20lakh%20in%20Bitcoin%20and%20Ethereum%2C%20apart%20from%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20that%20he%20used%20in%20altcoins%20like%20Shiba%20Inu%20and%20Dogecoin.%20But%20as%20bitcoin's%20price%20went%20on%20a%20tear%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20buy%20more%20-%20about%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20worth%20-%20on%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2022-year-old%20told%20the%20publication%20that%20he%20was%20up%20about%20Rs%2042%20lakh%20as%20the%20price%20of%20Bitcoin%20reached%20its%20all-time%20high.%20But%20at%20the%20end%20of%202021%20the%20crypto%20market%20took%20a%20turn%2C%20and%20by%20the%20summer%20of%202022%20bitcoin's%20price%20crashed%20over%2070%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20investing%20with%20some%20money%20that%20I%20didn't%20necessarily%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nguonly%20told%20%3Cem%3ECNBC%20Make%20It%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20crypto%20market%20kind%20of%20reversed%2C%20my%20losses%20were%20amplified.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20Mr.%20Nguonly%20doesn't%20necessarily%20regret%20the%20decision%20to%20invest%20in%20crypto%2C%20he%20borrowed%20money%20for%20investments.%20He%20continues%20to%20keep%20some%20money%20invested%20in%20cryptocurrency%20but%20sticks%20to%20historically%20more%20established%20tokens%20like%20Bitcoin%20and%20Ethereum%20versus%20the%20more%20volatile%20altcoins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20believe%20in%20cryptocurrencies%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20I%20do%20think%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20altcoins%20can%20be%20very%20risky%20and%20I%20avoid%20putting%20any%20money%20towards%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20lesson%20he%20learned%20from%20his%20Rs%2067%20lakh%20mistake%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bonly%20invest%20money%20you%20have%20and%20don't%20go%20un-leveraged%20into%20very%20speculative%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAlso%20Read%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Engineer%2C%2022%2C%20Plans%20To%20Retire%20At%2035%20With%20Savings%20Of%20%E2%82%B9%2041%20Crore.%20Here's%20How%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20interview%2C%20he%20told%20CNBC%20that%20he%20is%20aiming%20for%20an%20early%20retirement%20with%20a%20target%20of%20accumulating%20%245%20million%20(roughly%20Rs%2041%20crore)%20by%20the%20age%20of%2035.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695033240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F40cmfqso_google-generic_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgoogle-techie-22-loses-rs-67-lakh-to-crypto-scam-he-had-planned-to-retire-at-35-4400703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20techie%20shared%20that%20he%20lost%20Rs%2067%20lakh%20in%20crypto%20between%20November%202021%20and%20June%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgoogle-techie-22-loses-rs-67-lakh-to-crypto-scam-he-had