ated%20by%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENBDA%E2%80%99s%20odd%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association%20(NBDA)%20in%20a%20statement%20described%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20decision%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20dangerous%20precedent%E2%80%9D%20and%20went%20on%20to%20observe%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ban%20on%20representatives%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20from%20participating%20in%20TV%20news%20shows%20anchored%20by%20some%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20TV%20news%20personalities%20goes%20against%20the%20ethos%20of%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%20The%20usage%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cban%E2%80%9D%20in%20its%20statement%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners%20not%20to%20send%20their%20representatives%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20programmes%20anchored%20by%20those%2014%20anchors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NBDA%20also%20very%20strangely%20hailed%20those%20anchors%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20top%20TV%20news%20personalities%E2%80%9D%2C%20without%20in%20any%20way%20explaining%20the%20reasons%20for%20doing%20so.%20In%20its%20statement%2C%20the%20NBDA%20remarked%20that%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners%20%E2%80%9Cbetokens%20intolerance%20and%20imperils%20press%20freedom%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6betrays%20callous%20disregard%20for%20democracy%E2%80%99s%20most%20fundamental%20tenet%20%E2%80%93%20the%20inalienable%20right%20to%20openly%20express%20ideas%20and%20opinions%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20charged%20them%20of%20taking%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20nation%20back%20to%20the%20Emergency%20era%2C%20when%20the%20press%20was%20gagged%2C%20and%20independent%20opinions%20and%20voices%20were%20crushed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Boycott%20of%20'Godi'%20Anchors%20Raises%20Moral%20Concerns%2C%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Needs%20a%20More%20Subtle%20Approach%3A%20N%20Ram%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fwatch-boycott-of-godi-anchors-raises-moral-concerns-india-alliance-needs-a-more-subtle-approach-n-ram%5C%22%3EBoycott%20of%20%E2%80%98Godi%E2%80%99%20Anchors%20Raises%20Moral%20Concerns%2C%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Needs%20a%20More%20Subtle%20Approach%3A%20N%20Ram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20record%20of%20boycotting%20TV%20channels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20political%20parties%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20send%20their%20representatives%20to%20certain%20TV%20channels.%20There%20have%20been%20earlier%20examples%20of%20the%20BJP%20boycotting%20NDTV%20prior%20to%20Gautam%20Adani%20taking%20over%20the%20TV%20channel.%20Celebrated%20media%20personality%20N.%20Ram%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbBNk4YLkECM%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20interaction%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20consistently%20boycotting%20all%20TV%20channels%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20boycott%20is%20not%20based%20on%20any%20formal%20announcement.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20instructive%20that%20nobody%20has%20commented%20against%20the%20BJP%20for%20doing%20so%20in%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20NBDA%20has%20come%20down%20on%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%20appealed%20for%20boycotting%20newspapers%20spreading%20hate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20decided%20not%20to%20send%20their%20representatives%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20news%20programmes%20hosted%20by%2014%20anchors%20primarily%20because%20they%20used%20hate-filled%20remarks%20in%20a%20calculated%20manner%20in%20their%20newsrooms%20to%20engage%20in%20poisonous%20propaganda%20for%20promoting%20a%20communal%20agenda.%20Those%20partners%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20that%20agenda%20aimed%20at%20creating%20communal%20division%20and%20inciting%20religious%20sentiments%20which%20eventually%20would%20tear%20apart%20the%20unity%20and%20solidarity%20of%20people%20regardless%20of%20the%20faiths%20they%20pursued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20decision%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners%20echoes%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%201926%20appeal%20to%20people%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20newspapers%20which%20carried%20hate-filled%20content%20and%20wrought%20havoc%20to%20communal%20harmony.%20It%20is%20illuminating%20to%20note%20he%20issued%20that%20appeal%20for%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6purging%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20mutual%20hatred%20and%20calumny%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20%E2%80%9Cboycotting%20papers%20which%20foment%20hatred%20and%20spread%20misrepresentation%E2%80%9D.%20He%20persuasively%20put%20forth%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20would%20lose%20nothing%20if%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20papers%20were%20to%20cease%20today%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20so%20while%20moving%20a%20resolution%20on%20December%2026%2C%201926%20at%20the%20Gauhati%20session%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20expressing%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6horror%20and%20indignation%20at%20the%20cowardly%20and%20treacherous%20murder%20of%20Swami%20Shraddhanand%E2%80%9D%20and%20placing%20%E2%80%9Con%20record%20its%20sense%20of%20the%20irreparable%20loss%20the%20nation%20has%20sustained%20by%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20a%20brave%20and%20noble%20patriot%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwami%20Shraddhanand%20was%20assassinated%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20December%201926%20by%20one%20Abdul%20Rashid%20who%20came%20to%20interview%20Swamiji%20about%20his%20understanding%20of%20Islam.%20Rashid%20asked%20for%20some%20water%20to%20drink%20before%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20interview.%20As%20Swami%E2%80%99s%20servant%20went%20to%20fetch%20water%2C%20Rashid%20took%20out%20his%20revolver%20and%20fatally%20fired%20at%20him.%20Gandhi%20took%20a%20stand%20that%20the%20hate%20and%20hostility%20spread%20by%20the%20newspapers%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%20deeply%20poisoned%20Rashid%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20In%20his%20article%20%E2%80%9CShraddhanandji-%20The%20Martyr%E2%80%9D%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20December%2030%2C%201926%2C%20he%20wrote%20about%20the%20role%20played%20by%20newspapers%20in%20disrupting%20communal%20harmony%20by%20spreading%20hate%20and%20violence.%20Those%20words%20of%20Gandhi%20assume%20enormous%20significance%20in%20the%20context%20of%20India%20of%202023%20witnessing%20a%20demonic%20upsurge%20in%20religious%20polarisation%20caused%2C%20among%20others%2C%20by%20TV%20channels%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98Godi%20media%E2%80%99%2C%20incessantly%20peddling%20poisonous%20narratives%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGandhi%20forcefully%20asserted%20in%20the%20aforementioned%20article%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20newspaper%20man%20has%20become%20a%20walking%20plague%E2%80%9D%20and%20claimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20spreads%20the%20contagion%20of%20lies%20and%20calumnies.%E2%80%9D%20He%20further%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20exhausts%20the%20foul%20vocabulary%20of%20his%20dialect%2C%20and%20injects%20his%20virus%20into%20the%20unsuspecting%2C%20and%20often%20receptive%20minds%20of%20his%20readers%E2%80%9D.%20Gandhi%20then%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CLeaders%20%E2%80%98intoxicated%20with%20the%20exuberance%20of%20their%20own%20language%E2%80%99%20have%20not%20known%20to%20put%20a%20curb%20upon%20their%20tongues%20or%20pens%E2%80%9D.%20He%20remarked%20with%20pain%20and%20anguish%2C%20%E2%80%9CSecret%20and%20insidious%20propaganda%20has%20done%20its%20dark%20and%20horrible%20work%2C%20unchecked%20and%20unabashed%2C%E2%80%9D.%20Gandhi%20then%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20we%20the%20educated%20and%20the%20semi-educated%20class%20that%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20hot%20fever%20which%20possessed%20Abdul%20Rashid%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Csecret%20and%20insidious%20propaganda%E2%80%9D%20caused%20by%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20contagion%20of%20lies%20and%20calumnies%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20newspaper%20man%20of%201926%20has%20been%20multiplied%20manifold%20by%20the%20Godi%20Media%20and%20most%20TV%20channels%2C%20whose%20anchors%20are%20now%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20sources%20of%20the%20hate-filled%20campaign%20against%20people%20based%20on%20the%20religion%20they%20profess.%20Therefore%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20for%20boycott%20of%20newspapers%20transmitting%20hatred%20resonates%20in%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20decision%20not%20to%20send%20their%20representatives%20to%20take%20part%20in%20programmes%20hosted%20by%2014%20TV%20anchors%20who%20are%20accused%20of%20propagating%20a%20hate-driven%20agenda.%20Possibly%20for%20this%20reason%2C%20the%20partners%20described%20their%20decision%20as%20a%20form%20of%20%3Cem%3Esatyagraha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20non-cooperation%2C%20invoking%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695032459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30160235%2FGandhi-1944.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CIndia%20would%20lose%20nothing%20if%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20papers%20were%20to%20cease%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20then.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Happens%20To%20Old%20Parliament%20Building%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20parliament%20proceedings%20will%20move%20to%20the%20new%20building%20f