are%20scheduled%20to%20meet%20PM%20Modi%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20list%20of%20eight%20bills%20which%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20for%20discussion%20in%20the%20special%20session%20was%20given%20to%20the%20opposition%20by%20the%20government%20in%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0The%20controversial%20bill%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20election%20officers%2C%20which%20was%20previously%20believed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20agenda%2C%20was%20dropped%20amid%20protests%20by%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20initiatied%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20'Parliamentary%20journey%20of%2075%20years%20starting%20from%20Samvidhan%20Sabha%20-%20achievements%2C%20experiences%2C%20memories%20and%20learnings'%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20Parliament%20shifting%20to%20the%20new%20building%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bbidding%20goodbye%20to%20this%20building%20is%20an%20emotional%20moment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20from%20the%20times%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20to%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20they%20have%20given%20new%20direction%20to%20the%20nation%20under%20their%20leadership%20and%20today%20is%20an%20occasion%20to%20highlight%20their%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695031380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2F6hgoalm_narendra-modi-amit-shah-pti_625x300_01_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-meeting-of-union-cabinet-today-amid-parliament-special-session-4400454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20key%20meeting%20of%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20has%20been%20called%20this%20evening%20at%206%3A30%20pm%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20Parliament's%20five-day%20special%20session%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20though%20the%20agenda%20is%20not%20known%20yet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-meeting-of-union-cabinet-today-amid-parliament-special-session-4400454%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-meeting-of-union-cabinet-today-amid-parliament-special-session-4400454%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-meeting-of-union-cabinet-today-amid-parliament-special-session-4400454%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TRAI%20Consultation%20on%20OTT%20Regulation%20Has%20Consequences%20Beyond%20Net%20Neutrality%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18151637%2Fglenn-carstens-peters-EOQhsfFBhRk-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trai.gov.in%2Fconsultation-paper-regulatory-mechanism-over-top-ott-communication-services-and-selective-banning%5C%22%3Econsultation%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Telecom%20Regulatory%20Authority%20of%20India%20(TRAI)%20about%20regulatory%20mechanisms%20for%20Over%20The%20Top%20(OTT)%20communication%20services%20and%20select%20banning%20of%20these%20services%20has%20created%20a%20stir%20around%20net%20neutrality.%20TRAI%20raised%20many%20questions%2C%20one%20being%20the%20impact%20on%20net%20neutrality%20if%20OTTs%20were%20to%20tie%20up%20with%20telecom%20players%20or%20required%20to%20pay%20them%20based%20on%20traffic%20or%20bandwidth.%20Beyond%20net%20neutrality%2C%20this%20consultation%20has%20consequences%20on%20privacy%2C%20encryption%2C%20internet%20shutdowns%20and%20may%20create%20a%20new%20internet%20regime%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETRAI%20has%20been%20requested%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecom%20to%20address%20issues%20around%20regulation%20of%20OTTs%20with%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Communication%20and%20Information%20Technology%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20on%20selective%20banning%20of%20OTTs%20as%20an%20alternative%20for%20shutdowns.%20This%20has%20effectively%20opened%20up%20a%20host%20of%20issues%20on%20regulation%20of%20OTTs%20under%20the%20telecommunications%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20regards%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20net%20neutrality%2C%20telecom%20service%20providers%20(TSPs)%20in%20India%20want%20OTTs%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20capital%20expenditure%20of%205G%20expansion%20as%20they%20also%20pay%20a%20licensing%20fee%20to%20DoT.%20OTT%20communication%20services%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20Telegram%2C%20Signal%20and%20other%20apps%20have%20cut%20into%20the%20revenues%20of%20TSPs%20while%20not%20paying%20any%20of%20these%20extra%20licensing%20costs.%20The%20demand%20for%20a%20fee%20from%20OTTs%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20network%20expansion%20is%20considered%20unfair%20when%20customers%20are%20already%20paying%20for%20telecom%20services.%20A%20demand%20for%20any%20form%20of%20network%20fee%20would%20violate%20net%20neutrality%20and%20thus%20will%20limit%20the%20emergence%20of%20new%20OTTs%20by%20giving%20preferential%20treatment%20to%20the%20ones%20paying%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20around%20net%20neutrality%20was%20settled%20earlier%20with%20the%20fight%20against%20Free%20Basics-Internet.org%20and%20the%20general%20public%20opposition%20to%20Facebook%20becoming%20the%20gatekeeper.%20Those%20conditions%20that%20allowed%20the%20general%20public%20to%20champion%20digital%20rights%20do%20not%20exist%20today%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20net%20neutrality%20being%20repealed%20in%20some%20form%20does%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20been%20actively%20expanding%20regulations%20to%20stop%20Big%20Tech%20firms%E2%80%99%20practices%20and%20has%20been%20actively%20promoting%20Indian%20alternatives.%20Limiting%20Facebook%E2%80%99s%20plans%20around%20the%20internet%20in%20India%20has%20been%20beneficial%20for%20Indian%20startups%20and%20other%20internet%20companies.%20But%20the%20current%20demand%20against%20net%20neutrality%20is%20domestic%2C%20it%20can%20also%20hurt%20Indian%20IT%20firms%20if%20they%20are%20subjected%20to%20the%20same%20regulatory%20setup.%20What%20form%20this%20regulation%20takes%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20but%20a%20fee%20for%20foreign%20firms%20and%20a%20relaxation%20for%20Indian%20organisations%20in%20some%20measure%20can%20also%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20issue%20of%20net%20neutrality%2C%20it%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20licensing%20conditions%20of%20OTT%20communication%20services%20like%20WhatsApp%20and%20Signal%20that%20will%20be%20most%20concerning.%20The%20demand%20to%20regulate%20OTTs%20is%20coming%20as%20an%20alternative%20solution%20to%20internet%20shutdowns.%20If%20applications%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20Facebook%20or%20Twitter%20can%20be%20temporarily%20blocked%20during%20emergencies%2C%20then%20there%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20complete%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20is%20the%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20block%20these%20apps%20temporarily%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20do%20this%20would%20be%20to%20build%20a%20Chinese-style%20Great%20Internet%20Firewall%20to%20inspect%20all%20the%20networks%20for%20real-time%20censorship.%20BSNL%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trai.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FBharat_Sanchar_04092023.pdf%5C%22%3Eresponse%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20consultation%20paper%20has%20concluded%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20ban%20specific%20OTT%20services.%20But%20such%20an%20infrastructure%20can%20technically%20be%20built%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%205G%20telecom%20expansion%20could%20be%20the%20place%20where%20this%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ECurrent%20dimensioning%20of%20TSP%20infrastructure%20had%20not%20envisaged%20such%20type%20of%20deep%20packet%20inspection%20at%20the%20time%20of%20roll%20out%20of%20its%20network.%20Implementation%20of%20selective%20banning%20of%20OTT%20will%20impact%20the%20processing%20power%20of%20resources%20and%20huge%20augmentation%20in%20processing%20power%20will%20be%20required%20at%20TSP%20end.%20It%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%20such%20type%20of%20selective%20barring%20can%20be%20done%20for%20limited%20time%20for%20limited%20OTT%20services.%20There%20will%20be%20need%20to%20define%20this%20time%20period%20and%20limit%20of%20number%20of%20OTT%20service%20to%20be%20banned%20at%20a%20time%2C%20this%20will%20help%20to%20designing%20and%20expanding%20the%20TSP%20infrastructure%20accordingly%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20BSNL%20response%20on%20selective%20banning%20of%20OTTs%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20aspect%20of%20this%20regulation%20is%20also%20how%20it%20will%20regulate%20end-to-end%20encrypted%20systems%20for%20internal%20security%20requirements.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trai.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FGloba_%2520Encryption_Coalition_Steering_01092023.pdf%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Encryption%20Coalition%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20concerned%20with%20TRAI%E2%80%99s%20plans%20for%20regulation%20of%20OTTs%20and%20the%20consequences%20on%20encryption.%20At%20present%2C%20Section%2069%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20does%20give%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20powers%20to%20intercept%20and%20decrypt%20encrypted%20content.%20For%20a%20long%20time%20the%20question%20of%20WhatsApp%20encryption%20and%20the%20need%20to%20identify%20the%20contents%20of%20messages%20spreading%20hate%20and%20misinformation%20has%20been%20debated%20in%20our%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20TRAI%20consultation%20recommendations%20will%20determine%20whether%20India%20adopts%20a%20new%20telecom%20regime.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20we%20have%20opened%20these%20conversations%2C%20but%20with%20the%20new%20Telecom%20Bill%20likely%20to%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%20these%20consultations%20will%20determine%20the%20fate%20of%20Indians%20digital%20rights.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdot.gov.in%2Frelatedlinks%2Findian-telecommunication-bill-2022%5C%22%3Edraft%20Indian%20Telecommunications%20Bill%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20already%20has%20several%20provisions%20concerning%20the%20TRAI%E2%80%99s%20present%20consultation%2C%20some%20of%20those%20provisions%20are%20expected%20to%20change%20before%20it%20is%20introduced%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20host%20of%20these%20regulatory%20demands%20will%20likely%20be%20implemented%20in%20Manipur%20with%20the%20near%20complete%20internet%20shutdown%20in%20the%20state.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20road%20towards%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20could%20likely%20be%20with%20new%20OTT%20regulations%2C%20with%20no%20interest%20from%20any%20quarters%20to%20address%20the%20challenges%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20does%20push%20for%20regulation%20of%20OTTs%20registration%20in%20India%20or%20presses%20for%20additional%20costs%20for%20operations%2C%20several%20international%20companies%20are%20likely%20to%20exit%20the%20market.%20This%20is%20what%20happened%20when%20India%20brought%20its%20VPN%20rules%20asking%20VPN%20companies%20to%20maintain%20logs.%20One%20can%20term%20it%20going%20back%20to%20the%20licence%20raj%20era%2C%20with%20the%20increased%20regulations%20that%20are%20already%20under%20development%20limiting%20imports%20of%20computers%2C%20telecom%20equipment%20into%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695031242000%2C%22