tor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClimate%20finance%20and%20sustainability%20course%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20climate%20finance%20and%20sustainability%20course%20at%20IIT-Kanpur%20is%20designed%20to%20provide%20a%20thorough%20understanding%20of%20the%20critical%20connection%20between%20financial%20strategies%20and%20sustainable%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20aims%20to%20give%20professionals%20the%20information%20and%20abilities%20they%20need%20to%20successfully%20negotiate%20the%20complex%20world%20of%20sustainable%20business%20and%20climate%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERenewable%20energy%20and%20e-mobility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERenewable%20energy%20and%20e-mobility%20programme%20aims%20to%20empower%20professionals%20with%20expertise%20in%20renewable%20energy.%20The%20course%20is%20designed%20to%20give%20participants%20an%20in-depth%20understanding%20of%20sustainable%20energy%20systems%20and%20electric%20mobility%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticipants%20will%20be%20taught%20the%20principles%20of%20renewable%20energy%20and%20their%20practice%20in%20real-world%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20and%20machine%20learning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20course%2C%20students%20will%20acquire%20expertise%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20machine%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20AI%20and%20ML%20in%20practical%20applications%20will%20be%20taught%20to%20students%20through%20a%20variety%20of%20projects%20and%20case%20studies.%20This%20exercise%20will%20improve%20analytical%20and%20problem-solving%20abilities%2C%20preparing%20graduates%20to%20meet%20problems%20in%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20leadership%20in%20digital%20age%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20course%20aims%20to%20equip%20prospective%20professionals%20with%20a%20thorough%20understanding%20of%20contemporary%20business%20dynamics.%20It%20attempts%20them%20the%20knowledge