%2F18143010%2FIMG_0265-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673493%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20checkpoint%20has%20been%20set%20up%20in%20Dudkol%20village%20of%20Kokernag%20beyond%20which%20only%20locals%20are%20allowed%20while%20journalists%20have%20been%20pushed%20back%20from%20the%20site%20of%20the%20operation%20in%20Gadol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20operation%20has%20cast%20a%20spell%20of%20fear%20and%20gloom%20in%20Gadol%2C%20Dudkol%20and%20adjoining%20villages%20in%20Kokernag%20where%20the%20presence%20of%20security%20personnel%20has%20been%20stepped%20up.%20In%20a%20state%20of%20high%20alert%2C%20a%20paramilitary%20trooper%2C%20part%20of%20a%20road%20opening%20party%20involved%20in%20the%20operation%2C%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20foot%20%E2%80%9Caccidentally%E2%80%9D%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Dudkol%2C%20all%20the%20shops%20and%20other%20business%20establishments%20are%20shut%2C%20which%20has%20increased%20the%20difficulties%20of%20both%20locals%20as%20well%20as%20journalists%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20look%20forward%20to%20unsolicited%20cups%20of%20tea%20brought%20out%20by%20local%20residents%20who%20refuse%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media%20on%20the%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20several%20occasions%2C%20they%20came%20out%20with%20cups%20of%20tea%20without%20being%20asked.%20They%20are%20terrified%20by%20the%20situation%20and%20our%20presence%20perhaps%20gives%20them%20strength%20to%20carry%20on%20their%20normal%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bashir%20Ahmad%2C%20a%20cameraperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20difficulties%20and%20dangers%20of%20operating%20in%20an%20unknown%20terrain%2C%20security%20forces%20have%20been%20carrying%20out%20the%20operation%20with%20great%20caution%2C%20pounding%20the%20suspected%20hideouts%20with%20heavy%20explosives.%20High-tech%20gadgets%20like%20Heron%20drones%20have%20been%20used%20to%20target%20the%20hideouts.%20One%20vid