01%20was%20scrapped%20three%20days%20later.%20The%20reason%20-%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Congress%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20called%20out%20the%20hypocrisy%20of%20a%20unity%20extravaganza%2C%20at%20some%20cost%20to%20the%20party's%20fragile%20finances%2C%20when%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20were%20declaring%20their%20own%20candidates%20for%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20conveyed%20his%20clear%20message%20to%20the%20leadership%20and%20committed%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20unit's%20resources%20into%20launching%20seven%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EJan%20Aakrosh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(people's%20angst)%20%3Cem%3EYatras%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20across%20the%20state%20beginning%20on%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%20(September%2019).%20The%20choice%20of%20the%20date%20reflects%20Kamal%20Nath's%20competitive%20religiosity%20-%20his%20counter%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP's%20Hindutva.%20Nath%2C%20unlike%20central%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20had%20distanced%20himself%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Minister%20and%20DMK%20youth%20icon%20Udaynidhi%20Stalin's%20remarks%20against%20Sanatan%20Dharm%2C%20by%20asserting%20that%20%26quot%3BBharat%20is%20the%20nation%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharm%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20Nath%20had%20said%20that%20his%20fight%20was%20primarily%20aimed%20at%20countering%20the%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bsangathan%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E(organisation)%20of%20BJP%2C%20which%20axiomatically%20entails%20refurbishing%20the%20Congress's%3Cem%3E%20%26quot%3Bsangathan%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20His%20government%20was%20toppled%20by%20defections.%20A%20number%20of%20defectors%20who%20had%20joined%20the%20BJP%20with%20Jyotirdaditya%20Scindia%20in%202020%20have%2C%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20returned%20to%20the%20Congress%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%20regularly%20organises%20religious%20events%20in%20his%20borough%20of%20Chhindwara%2C%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20he%20represented%20nine%20times%201980%20onwards%20(His%20son%20Nakul%20is%20MP%20now).%20All%20nine%20assembly%20seats%20of%20Chhindwara%20are%20with%20the%20Congress%20(Nath%20represents%20Chhindwara%20in%20the%20state%20assembly).%20%26quot%3BWe%20go%20to%20the%20temple%20for%20our%20belief%20and%20not%20to%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20political%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20recently%20told%20an%20interviewer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20longstanding%20friend%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20(he%20was%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20Doon%20School%20contemporary)%20Nath%20has%20a%20good%20equation%20with%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20who%20is%20often%20seen%20at%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20events.%20Nath%20is%20the%20sole%20Congress%20satrap%20who%20retains%20a%20veneer%20of%20autonomy%20around%20his%20persona.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bhopal%20rally%20is%20not%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20one-liner%20with%20which%20Nath%20put%20paid%20to%20the%20plan%20charted%20by%20the%20coordination%20committee%20at%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Delhi%20residence%20last%20Thursday.%20The%20Congress%20is%20the%20dominant%20partner%20of%20the%20bloc%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20states%20where%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20have%20%26quot%3Bdominance%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Bloc%20also%20differ%20from%20the%20central%20leadership.%20West%20Bengal%20Congress%20chief%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20Punjab's%20leaders%20Amrinder%20Raja%20Warring%20and%20Pratap%20Singh%20Bajwa%2C%20Delhi's%20Ajay%20Maken%20and%20of%20late%2C%20new%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20president%20Ajai%20Rai%2C%20have%20been%20sounding%20notes%20of%20caution%20on%20ties%20with%20parties%20which%20have%20grown%20essentially%20by%20poaching%20on%20Congress%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20uncertainties%20and%20the%20extreme%20regional%20postures%20of%20these%20partners%20of%20the%20bloc%20have%20been%20worrying%20Congress%20leaders%20at%20the%20state%20level%20though%20the%20central%20leadership%20has%20been%20rooting%20for%20the%20bloc%2C%20which%20was%20reiterated%20at%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20reconstituted%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20in%20Hyderabad%20last%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20by-elections%2C%20INDIA%20constituents%20won%20four%20of%20the%20seven%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20faultlines%20were%20evident%20in%20each%20victory.%20In%20West%20Bengal's%20Dhupguri%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20ousted%20the%20CPI%20(M)%20candidate%20backed%20by%20the%20Congress%3B%20Puthupally%20in%20Kerala%20saw%20the%20Congress%20retain%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Late%20Oommen%20Chandy's%20seat%20in%20spite%20of%20incumbent%20CPI%20(M)%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan's%20strong%20campaign%20for%20his%20candidate.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20declared%20the%20Ghosi%20victory%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvictory%20for%20INDIA%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Ajai%20Rai%20questioned%20whether%20the%20defeat%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Bageshwar%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20candidate%20eating%20into%20his%20party's%20votes%2C%20was%20not%20a%20defeat%20for%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad%20-%20where%20Kamal%20Nath%20was%20not%20among%20the%2090%20attendees%20(35%20CWC%20members%20plus%20invitees)%20-%20passed%20a%20resolution%20heavily%20critical%20of%20the%20BJP%20regime%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20listing%20its%20%26quot%3Bfailures%26quot%3B%20across%20several%20fronts%20at%20home%20and%20abroad.%20It%20did%20not%20spell%20out%20an%20alternative%20vision%20that%20the%20Congress%20could%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20penchant%20for%20his%20%26quot%3BVision%20of%20India%26quot%3B%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20rhetoric%20that%20he%20relies%20upon%20while%20addressing%20audiences%20abroad%20but%20one%20that%20his%20party%20is%20at%20a%20loss%20to%20formulate.%20The%20Hyderabad%20meet%20did%20not%20chart%20a%20%26quot%3BCongress%20strategy%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20to%20reconnect%20with%20the%20electorate%20and%20regain%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyderabad%20was%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20CWC.%20He%20took%20seven%20months%20since%20being%20authorised%20by%20the%20party's%20Raipur%20plenary%20in%20February%20to%20reconstitute%20the%20leadership%20panel.%20A%20seasoned%20politician%20with%20five%20decades%20of%20electoral%20victories%20under%20his%20belt%2C%20Kharge%20continues%20to%20live%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20idiosyncrasies.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20appoint%20new%20central%20office%20bearers%2C%20though%20he%20has%20made%20some%20state-level%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIpso%20facto%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20extends%20all%20courtesy%20to%20the%20octogenarian%20Congress%20President.%20He%20even%20helps%20him%20climb%20stairs%20and%20holds%20his%20hand%20while%20he%20is%20getting%20onto%20a%20dais.%20In%20Paris%2C%20commenting%20on%20Kharge%20not%20being%20invited%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%20to%20the%20G20%20dinner%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20described%20him%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bleader%20of%2060%20per%20cent%20Indians%26quot%3B.%20(Congress%20won%2019%25%20votes%20in%202019.%20It%20has%2013%25%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20two%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%3B%2017%25%20of%20State%20legislators%20belong%20to%20Congress.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20scrutiny%20of%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu's%20guest%20list%20would%20show%20that%20BJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%20was%20not%20included%20either.%20Union%20Ministers%20and%20state%20Chief%20Ministers%20were%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETriggered%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20comment%2C%20three%20Congress%20Chief%20Ministers%20-%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20Siddaramaiah%20-%20gave%20the%20G20%20invite%20of%20the%20President%20a%20miss.%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Sukhvinder%20Sukhu%20attended%20and%20Narendra%20Modi's%20warmest%20hug%20seemed%20reserved%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20MK%20Stalin%20and%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20attended%20the%20dinner.%20Photos%20of%20all%20three%20being%20accorded%20appropriate%20courtesy%2C%20including%20being%20introduced%20to%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20appeared%20the%20next%20day.%20Apparently%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20abhorrence%20for%20G20%20(which%20he%20criticised%20abroad%20while%20the%20nation%20applauded)%20is%20not%20shared%20by%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20Bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vulnerability%20and%20fragility%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20apparent.%20Apart%20from%20the%20Congress's%20turf%20battles%20with%20regional%20parties%20and%20AAP%2C%20even%20CPI(M)%2C%20whose%20Secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20beacon%20on%20many%20issues%2C%20is%20demanding%20seats%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20four%20states%20that%20will%20vote%20later%20this%20year.%20The%20CPI%20(M)%20has%20not%20named%20its%20nominee%20to%20the%20bloc's%20coordination%20panel%20so%20far.%20The%20road%20to%20anti-BJP%20unity%20is%20riddled%20by%20potholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695027120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2Ff1kp1q58_kamal-nath-press-conference-march-2020-pti_625x300_20_March_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkamal-nath-shows-mirror-to-india-stalls-rally-4400199%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20road%20to%20anti-BJP%20unity%20is%20riddled%20by%20potholes.%