d%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Crenewal%20of%20the%20close%20bonds%20of%20cooperation%20and%20friendship%20with%20the%20election%20of%20Mr%20Solih%20as%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%9D.%20It%20even%20specifically%20mentions%20that%20Solih%20requested%20help%20from%20India%20to%20support%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20government%20in%20meeting%20its%20pledges%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%9D.%20India%20eagerly%20jumped%20in%2C%20announcing%20a%20series%20of%20development%20projects%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20outlying%20islands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20Solih%20went%20on%20an%20inauguration%20spree%20of%20small%20projects%20around%20Maldives%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20round%2C%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHCIMaldives%2Fstatus%2F1696812319186255901%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esome%20sponsored%20by%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20India%20spent%20Rs%201156.56%20crore%20in%20grants%20and%20loans%20to%20Maldives%20from%202018-19%20to%202021-22%2C%20as%20per%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20from%20the%20Union%20budget%20documents.%20This%20is%20an%20increase%20of%20165.18%25%20from%20the%20Rs%20436.13%20crore%20from%202013-14%20to%202017-18.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F15040518%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F15040518%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F15040518%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20year%202018-19%2C%20the%20allocation%20for%20Maldives%20in%20the%20budget%20estimates%20was%20Rs%20125%20crore.%20But%2C%20when%20the%20figures%20were%20revised%20for%20that%20year%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20November%202018%20election%20result%2C%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20allocation%20went%20up%20to%20Rs%20440%20crore.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20for%20that%20year%20closely%20matched%20the%20revised%20allocation%2C%20totalling%20Rs%20439%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202020%2C%20India%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-india-china-funding-infrastructure-jaishankar-abdulla-shahid%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20it%20will%20fund%20the%20Greater%20Male%20Connectivity%20Project%2C%20the%20largest%20civilian%20infrastructure%20project%20in%20Maldives.%20The%20ambitious%20completion%20date%20was%202023%2C%20but%20it%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmfr.mv%2Fpublic-sector%2Fphase-one-of-the-thilamale-bridge-to-be-completed-this-year%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erevised%20to%20mid-2024%20due%20to%20delays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20agreement%20to%20develop%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fexternal-affairs%2Futhuru-thilafalhu-utf-harbour-project-maldives-india-male-delhi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUthuru%20Thilafalhu%20atoll%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20a%20naval%20dockyard%20for%20Maldives%20fuelled%20thousands%20of%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20even%20as%20Mal%C3%A9%20went%20on%20the%20defensive%20amidst%20domestic%20calls%20for%20releasing%20the%20full%20details%20of%20the%20agreement.%20The%20Maldivian%20National%20Defence%20Forces%20arranged%20a%20trip%20of%20local%20journalists%20this%20weekend%20to%20the%20atoll%20to%20refute%20allegations%20that%20it%20will%20be%20turned%20into%20an%20Indian%20base.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20India%20apparently%20resonating%20among%20voters%2C%20there%20is%20now%20a%20question%20mark%20around%20India%E2%80%99s%20development%20diplomacy%20in%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20India%20has%20caused%20to%20worry%20about%20relations%20under%20a%20Muizzu%20presidency%2C%20observers%20are%20also%20not%20convinced%20that%20it%20would%20be%20a%20smooth%20ride%20for%20a%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20presidency.%20Even%20after%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20judiciary%20will%20not%20accept%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20to%20stand%20for%20election%20due%20to%20conviction%2C%20his%20first%20choice%20had%20been%20to%20ask%20his%20party%20to%20boycott%20the%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20housing%20minister%20had%20to%20resign%20from%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20and%20join%20the%20alliance%20partner%2C%20People%E2%80%99s%20National%20Congress%2C%20which%20nominated%20him%20as%20presidential%20candidate.%20Yameen%20then%20accepted%20him%20as%20fait%20accompli.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%20has%20pledged%20to%20overturn%20President%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20conviction%20if%20he%20secures%20the%20presidency.%20However%2C%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20return%20would%20mean%20that%20he%20would%20dominate%20the%20government%2C%20which%20could%20potentially%20lead%20to%20tensions%20with%20Muizzu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20that%20is%20speculative%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20the%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives-People%E2%80%99s%20National%20Congress%20candidate%20enthusiastic%20advocate%20for%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20that%20highlights%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98close%E2%80%99%20associations%20with%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20his%20election%20rallies%2C%20Muizzu%20said%20multiple%20times%20that%20he%20would%