%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20there%20is%20no%20one%20correct%20path%20to%20resistance%2C%20but%20that%20there%20are%20many%20different%20streams%20that%20make%20up%20a%20mighty%20river.%20The%20example%20of%20our%20independence%20movement%20proves%20just%20that.%20It%20was%20not%20one%20movement%2C%20but%20many%2C%20that%20reinforced%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20its%20major%20leaders%2C%20whether%20Jinnah%2C%20Gandhi%2C%20Patel%2C%20Bose%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Azad%20%E2%80%93%20were%20at%20loggerheads%20often%20enough%2C%20with%20some%20differences%20that%20became%20insurmountable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20also%20that%20iconic%20comment%20of%20Malcolm%20X%20to%20Loretta%20Scott%20King%2C%20in%20Selma%2C%20when%20Malcolm%20%E2%80%93%20mere%20weeks%20before%20his%20assassination%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdigital.wustl.edu%2Fe%2Feii%2Feiiweb%2Fkin5427.0224.089corettascottking.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20her%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20Selma%20to%20make%20his%20job%20more%20difficult%20but%20I%20thought%20that%20if%20the%20White%20people%20understood%20what%20the%20alternative%20was%20that%20they%20would%20be%20more%20inclined%20to%20listen%20to%20your%20husband.%20And%20so%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20came.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20are%20to%20overcome%20this%20moment%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20troubled%20history%2C%20we%20will%20need%20to%20do%20so%20together%2C%20despite%20our%20differences%20in%20approach.%20The%20constant%20critique%20that%20not%20everybody%20standing%20up%20is%20being%20the%20perfect%20politician%20is%20unhelpful.%20We%20do%20not%2C%20and%20should%20not%2C%20aspire%20to%20be%20a%20country%20of%20only%20perfect%20politicians%2C%20but%20of%20people%20free%20to%20pursue%20their%20joys%20in%20multiple%20ways%20without%20harming%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20is%20not%20your%20martyr%2C%20please%20stop%20asking%20him%20to%20be%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fomair-ahmad%5C%22%3EOmair%20Ahmad%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20author%20and%20journalist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695022549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07202344%2FScreenshot-2023-09-07-at-8.18.32-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fshah-rukh-khan-is-not-your-martyr%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20political%20load%20that%20the%20Indian%20star%20is%20being%20forced%20to%20carry%20is%20not%20his%20to%20bear.%20Allow%20him%20to%20be%20free%20to%20be%20himself.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fshah-rukh-khan-is-not-your-martyr%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliament%20LIVE%3A%20Nehru's%20'tryst%20with%20destiny'%20still%20inspires%20us%2C%20says%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695021148000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F26%2Ffull%2F1685119265-3421.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-special-session-live-houses-to-hold-discussion-on-parliamentary-journey-123091800069_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20parliament%20is%20set%20to%20meet%20for%20a%20special%20five-day%20session%2C%20catch%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-ne