2%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fspecial-session-emotional-moment-to-leave-old-parliament-says-pm-modi-123091800302_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fspecial-session-emotional-moment-to-leave-old-parliament-says-pm-modi-123091800302_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fspecial-session-emotional-moment-to-leave-old-parliament-says-pm-modi-123091800302_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Vishwakarma%20Scheme%20for%20Artisans%20Draws%20Mixed%20Responses%20From%20OBC%20Groups%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18122433%2FF6OTQs9XAAAAvVO.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20Sunday%20(September%2017)%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20launched%20the%20PM%20Vishwakarma%20scheme%20to%20provide%20loans%2C%20training%20and%20marketing%20support%20to%20artisan%20communities.%20However%2C%20the%20scheme%20has%20drawn%20conflicting%20reactions%20from%20leaders%20of%20OBC%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERs%2013%2C000%20crore%20have%20been%20earmarked%20for%20the%20scheme%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%2C%20with%20government%20aiming%20to%20reach%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fcurrent-affairs%2F180923%2Fpm-modi-launches-pm-vishwakarma-scheme-inaugurates-yashobhoomi-conv.html%5C%22%3Eabout%2030%20lakh%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20traditional%20artisans%20and%20craftsmen%2C%20including%20weavers%2C%20goldsmiths%2C%20blacksmiths%2C%20laundry%20workers%2C%20and%20barbers.%20People%20involved%20in%2018%20specific%20trades%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20loans%20up%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20at%205%25%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20was%20first%20announced%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20on%20August%2015.%20%E2%80%9COn%20this%20Vishwakarma%20Jayanti%2C%20we%20will%20give%20about%20Rs%2013%2C000-15%2C000%20crore%20to%20the%20people%20who%20live%20with%20traditional%20skills%2C%20who%20work%20with%20tools%20and%20with%20their%20own%20hands%2C%20mostly%20from%20the%20OBC%20community.%20Be%20it%20our%20carpenters%2C%20our%20goldsmiths%2C%20our%20masons%2C%20our%20laundry%20workers%2C%20our%20barber%20brothers%2C%20and%20sisters%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20leaders%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fnarendra-modi-launches-pm-vishwakarma-scheme-artisan-aid-splits-obc-leaders%2Fcid%2F1967009%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20believe%20that%20this%20scheme%20will%20reinforce%20caste-based%20occupations%20and%20deny%20community%20members%20real%20progress.%20Others%2C%20however%2C%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20important%20welfare%20measure%20for%20ignored%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20scheme%20will%20not%20help%20people%20from%20the%20artisan%20castes%20lead%20comfortable%20lives.%20It%20will%20deny%20them%20real%20progress%2C%E2%80%9D%20P.C.%20Patanjali%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Most%20Backward%20Classes%20Forum%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20people%20largely%20migrate%20from%20the%20villages%20to%20the%20cities%20to%20escape%20the%20stigma%20attached%20to%20their%20caste-based%20occupations%2C%20and%20to%20seek%20better%20lives%20and%20better%20education%20for%20their%20children.%20The%20new%20scheme%20will%20push%20them%20back%20into%20their%20(traditional)%20occupations%20in%20the%20villages%20and%20deprive%20their%20children%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20quality%20education.%20They%20can%20neither%20become%20entrepreneurs%20nor%20become%20part%20of%20mainstream%20education%20or%20administration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20believes%20that%20the%20amounts%20being%20offered%20under%20the%20scheme%20will%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20actually%20help%20community%20members%20build%20better%20lives.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20should%20have%20identified%20the%20artisan%20castes%2C%20exempted%20them%20from%20the%20creamy%20layer%2C%20and%20provided%20additional%20support%20through%20scholarships%2C%20residential%20schooling%20and%20coaching%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patanjali%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20aspiring%20entrepreneurs%20should%20have%20been%20provided%20with%20help%20to%20acquire%20and%20use%20advanced%20technologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHansaraj%20Jangra%2C%20president%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Backward%20Classes%20Federation%2C%20and%20Sanjay%20Harshwal%20from%20the%20Jangid%20Brahmin%20Mahasabha%20(an%20OBC%20rights%20group)%2C%20told%20The%20Telegraph%20that%20the%20scheme%20was%20a%20welcome%20development.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20should%20have%20started%20this%20scheme%20at%20least%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20but%20better%20late%20than%20never%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harshwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695020134000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18122433%2FF6OTQs9XAAAAvVO.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-vishwakarma-scheme-for-artisans-draws-mixed-responses-from-obc-groups%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20leaders%20believe%20that%20this%20scheme%20will%20reinforce%20caste-based%20occupations%20and%20deny%20community%20members%20real%20progress.%20Others%2C%20however%2C%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20important%20welfare%20measure%20for%20ignored%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-vishwakarma-scheme-for-artisans-draws-mixed-responses-from-obc-groups%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20and%20its%20allies%20battle%20Russian%20bid%20to%20have%20genocide%20case%20tossed%20out%20of%20the%20United%20