3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-66816893.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-66816893.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Significant%20Insensitivity'%3A%20Union%20Govt%20Mulls%20Withdrawal%20of%20RAF%20From%20Manipur%2C%20Says%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18111206%2FF3f08SBWcAEV7mk.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20could%20be%20withdrawing%20personnel%20of%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Forces%20from%20Manipur%2C%20where%20they%20are%20among%20security%20forces%20deployed%20to%20control%20the%20brutal%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-to-withdraw-rapid-action-force-from-manipur%2Farticle67318269.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20told%20by%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccontinuous%20exposure%20of%20the%20RAF%20to%20the%20anti-insurgency%20theatre%20may%20be%20not%20suitable%20for%20a%20force%20trained%20in%20crowd%20control%20and%20law%20and%20order%20duties%2C%20including%20agitation%20and%20communal%20incidents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%20had%20said%20in%20statement%20then%20that%20%E2%80%9Cone%20rioter%20was%20killed%20while%20few%20others%20were%20injured%20during%20the%20failed%20attempt%E2%80%9D%20to%20loot%20weapons%20from%20the%20India%20Reserve%20Battalion%20(IRB)%20at%20Khangabok%20in%20Thoubal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%2010%20companies%20of%20the%20RAF%20are%20deployed%20in%20the%20state%20which%20is%20sharply%20divided%20along%20ethnic%20lines%20now.%20Among%20the%2010%2C%20eight%20are%20in%20the%20Valley%20districts%20and%20two%20are%20in%20the%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20a%20whopping%2036%2C000%20paramilitary%20and%20Army%20soldiers%20are%20deployed%20in%20Manipur%20at%20present.%20Of%20them%2C%20two%20Border%20Security%20Forces%20jawans%20and%20an%20Army%20soldier%20on%20leave%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViolence%20has%20escalated%20after%20a%20brief%20lull%2C%20leading%20to%20fresh%20deployment%20of%20security%20forces%20in%20areas%20where%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20settlements%20are%20adjacent%20and%20which%20have%20seen%20the%20maximum%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20has%20highlighted%20a%20recent%20internal%20RAF%20report%20noting%20that%20it%20was%20attacked%20with%20%E2%80%9Cglass%20balls%2C%20stones%2C%20sharp%20iron%20rods%20and%20petrol%20bombs%E2%80%9D%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20stop%20a%20mob%20of%20around%203%2C000%20persons%20from%20looting%20weapons%20from%20a%20police%20armoury%20in%20Thoubal%20in%20early%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20internal%20report%20has%20also%20noted%2C%20with%20the%20example%20of%20this%20Thoubal%20incident%2C%20that%20senior%20police%20officers%20and%20local%20magistrates%20often%20do%20not%20visit%20such%20incident%20spots%2C%20demonstrating%20what%20the%20RAF%20calls%20is%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20insensitivity%20and%20lack%20of%20coordination%20resulting%20in%20mismanaged%20crowd%20control%20and%20handling%20of%20serious%20conflicts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20RAF%20is%20trained%20to%20use%20minimal%20fire%20power%20and%20is%20meant%20to%20act%20quickly%20to%20diffuse%20situations%20with%20%E2%80%9Cminimal%20lethality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20RAF%20is%20unarmed%20and%20their%20deployment%20in%20Manipur%20is%20%E2%80%9Cexposing%20them%20as%20a%20bigger%20target%20for%20firearms%20of%20miscreants%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManipur%20Police%20and%20the%20central%20forces%20have%20emerged%20at%20odds%20with%20each%20other%2C%20with%20the%20Kuki%20community%20accusing%20the%20former%20of%20siding%20with%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Meitei%20community%20accusing%20the%20latter%20of%20favouring%20Kukis.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20personnel%20of%20the%209th%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%5C%22%3Ebattalion%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20paramilitary%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695015945000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18111206%2FF3f08SBWcAEV7mk.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-raf-police-paramilitary-riot%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hindu%20has%20reported%20that%20it%20was%20told%20by%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20that%20continuous%20exposure%20of%20the%20RAF%20to%20the%20anti-insurgency%20theatre%20may%20be%20not%20suitable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-raf-police-paramilitary-riot%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22STOCK%20MARKET%20LIVE%3A%20Smallcaps%20swim%20in%20green%3B%20IOB%20zooms%2014%25%2C%20Uco%20Bank%2010%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695015541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F17%2Ffull%2F1681717052-5907.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-today-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-gift-nifty-us-stocks-fed-meet-share-market-updates-123091800062_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20Update%20on%20Monday%2C%20September%2018%3A%20Broader%20indices%2C%20were%20mixed%2C%20the%20BSE%20MidCap%20index%20was%20more-or-less%20unmoved%2C%20while%20the%20SmallCap%20index%20was%20up%200.2%20per