2Fem%3E.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20marking%20Azadi%20ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%20and%20have%20entered%20into%20Amrit%20Kaal%2C%20the%2025-year-long%20lead%20up%20to%20India%40100%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20term%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20was%20first%20used%20by%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20his%20speech%20from%20the%20Red%20Fort%20on%20August%2015%2C%202021%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Independence%20day.%20Elaborating%20on%20the%20concept%2C%20the%20he%20had%20said%20that%20Amrit%20Kaal%20aimed%20to%20improve%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20citizens%20of%20India%2C%20lessen%20the%20divide%20in%20development%20between%20villages%20and%20cities%2C%20reduce%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20interference%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20and%20welcome%20the%20latest%20technology.%C2%A0%20Modi%20further%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CStarting%20from%20here%2C%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20next%2025%20years%20is%20the%20Amrit%20Kaal%20of%20a%20new%20India.%20The%20fulfilment%20of%20our%20resolutions%20in%20this%20Amrit%20Kaal%20will%20take%20us%20till%20100%20years%20of%20independence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMilton%20Friedman%2C%20the%20famous%20economist%2C%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20great%20mistakes%20is%20to%20judge%20policies%20and%20programs%20by%20their%20intention%20rather%20than%20their%20results%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20the%20intent%20of%20what%20the%20prime%20minster%20has%20said%20is%20noble.%20However%2C%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20assessed%20is%20whether%20these%20intents%20are%20achievable%3F%20What%20are%20the%20accentuating%20factors%20that%20may%20impede%20achievement%20of%20the%20aim%20and%20how%20to%20overcome%20those%20impediments%3F%20Another%20factor%20that%20we%20have%20to%20consider%20is%20the%20record%20of%20delivery%20of%20the%20assurances%20made%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%209%20years%20don%E2%80%99t%20inspire%20confidence.%20Even%20if%20the%20promises%20of%20recovering%20black%20money%20and%20depositing%20Rs%2015%20lakhs%20in%20bank%20account%20of%20everyone%20are%20considered%20flippancy%2C%20there%20are%20many%20other%20promises%20like%20reigning%20in%20inflation%2C%20reduction%20of%20prices%20of%20LPG%20and%20fuel%2C%20strengthening%20of%20Rupee%20against%20Dollar%2C%20reducing%20poverty%2C%20doubling%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20income%20by%202022%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ehar%20ghar%20nal%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20many%20more%20remain%20unrealised.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20we%20now%20have%20the%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20of%20world%2C%20we%20remain%20way%20down%20in%20the%20list%20in%20regard%20to%20per%20capita%20income.%20The%20government%20itself%20admits%20that%20they%20are%20compelled%20to%20give%20subsistence%20ration%20of%20five%20kgs%20every%20month%20free%20of%20cost%20to%20almost%2080%20crore%20people.%20The%20fact%20that%20these%20promises%20could%20not%20be%20fulfilled%20indicates%20that%20the%20planners%20failed%20to%20take%20such%20variables%20into%20account%20which%20may%20have%20adversely%20impacted%20achievement%20of%20those%20objectives.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20some%20of%20the%20factors%20were%20totally%20unexpected%2C%20like%20the%20prolonged%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20However%2C%20some%20other%20causative%20factors%20were%20self-inflicted%2C%20like%20the%20ill-conceived%20demonetisation%20in%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20leaders%20therefore%20have%20to%20consider%20all%20factors%20and%20prepare%20tangible%20action%20plans%20to%20overcome%20these%20impediments%20if%20India%20is%20to%20celebrate%20100%20years%20of%20independence%20as%20a%20progressive%20and%20prosperous%20nation%20in%202047.%20Mere%20pronouncement%20of%20intent%20isn%E2%80%99t%20adequate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20founding%20fathers%20laid%20such%20strong%20foundations%20that%20the%20nation%20progressed%20in%20leaps%20and%20bounds%20in%20last%2076%20years.%20During%20this%20period%20our%20economy%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20the%20fifth%20largest%20in%20the%20world%20and%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%20Tremendous%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20in%20creation%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20industrial%20production%20and%20the%20service%20sector.%20Our%20IITs%20and%20IIMs%20are%20rated%20amongst%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20and%20have%20produced%20many%20bright%20individuals%20who%20have%20excelled%20not%20only%20at%20the%20national%20level%20but%20also%20internationally.%20Several%20alumni%20of%20these%20institutions%20are%20heading%20important%20world%20institutions%20including%20the%20IMF.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjournalism-in-modis-amrit-kaal-is-risky-business%5C%22%3E%20Journalism%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20Is%20Risky%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20India%20achieved%20all%20this%20in-spite%20of%20many%20external%20aggressions%20from%20two%20of%20our%20neighbours%20during%20these%20years%20speaks%20for%20the%20strength%20and%20resilience%20of%20our%20economy%20and%20national%20will.%20Our%20political%20and%20military%20leadership%20displayed%20their%20resolve%20by%20facing%C2%A0%20these%20aggressions%20and%20coming%20out%20with%20flying%20colours.%20Several%20insurgencies%20in%20the%20North%20East%20have%20been%20resolved%20amicably%20by%20a%20mix%20of%20security%20and%20population%20centric%20measures%20except%20for%20Manipur%20which%20has%20witnessed%20large%20scale%20ethnic%20violence%20for%20over%20four%20months.%20The%20Maoist%20insurgency%20in%20central%20India%20continues%20to%20rage%20even%20though%20the%20level%20of%20violence%20has%20drastically%20reduced.%20That%20there%20have%20been%20some%20hits%20and%20misses%20is%20only%20natural%20because%20of%20the%20vastness%20and%20diversity%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20tendency%20of%20humans%20to%20repeat%20the%20success%20of%20their%20last%20endeavour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20should%20not%20be%20difficult%20for%20the%20present%20and%20future%20leadership%20of%20India%20to%20take%20the%20nation%20to%20a%20stage%20where%20India%20stands%20at%20the%20front%20of%20comity%20of%20nations.%20However%2C%20for%20this%20to%20happen%20the%20leadership%20has%20to%20be%20forward%20thinking%20and%20formulate%20policies%20after%20war%20gaming%20futuristic%20scenarios.%20Such%20policies%20must%20conform%20to%20the%20changing%20environment%20and%20demands%20of%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeace%20and%20tranquility%20is%20the%20first%20requisite%20for%20realising%20the%20potential%20of%20India%20to%20become%20a%20leading%20world%20power.%20Several%20fault%20lines%20in%20our%20society%20which%20put%20heavy%20strain%20on%20our%20efforts%20to%20achieve%20our%20destiny%20must%20be%20addressed%20urgently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20major%20fault%20line%20that%20needs%20urgent%20attention%20is%20the%20increasing%20communalisation%20of%20our%20society.%20Besides%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fharyana-at-least-1-killed-5-injured-as-clashes-breakout-during-rally-by-hindutva-outfits-in-nuh%5C%22%3Eriots%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fthe-manipur-crisis-in-numbers-four-months-of-unending-violence%5C%22%3EManipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fharyana-at-least-1-killed-5-injured-as-clashes-breakout-during-rally-by-hindutva-outfits-in-nuh%5C%22%3EHaryana%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20cases%20of%20mob%20violence%20which%20are%20directly%20attributed%20to%20increasing%20radicalisation%20amongst%20masses.%20Religious%20processions%20with%20crowds%20carrying%20weapons%20while%20shouting%20provocative%20slogans%20end%20up%20disturbing%20peace%20and%20result%20in%20violence.%20Terms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-interface-of-love-and-jihad-is-a-false-indian-articulation%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Clove%20jihad%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fneo-khalistanis-cow-vigilantes-challenge-indias-security-establishment%5C%22%3Ecow%20vigilantism%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20are%20now%20in%20common%20lexicon.%20People%20involved%20in%20traditional%20cattle%20trade%20are%20wantonly%20attacked%20by%20alleging%20that%20the%20animals%20are%20being%20carried%20for%20slaughter.%20There%20are%20instances%20of%20people%20having%20been%20killed%20on%20mere%20suspicion%20meat%20in%20their%20fridge%20being%20beef!%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ethnic%20strife%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20inability%20of%20the%20government%20to%20contain%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20spiral%20out%20of%20control%20and%20may%20fuel%20secessionist%20tendencies%20in%20the%20North-East%20once%20again.%20The%20leaders%20must%20behave%20in%20statesman-like%20manner%20and%20rise%20above%20the%20parochial%20considerations%20of%20religion%2C%20ethnicity%20and%20language.%20The%20leaders%20must%20work%20towards%20emotional%20integration%20of%20people%20from%20all%20regions%2C%20religions%20and%20ethnicity.%20The%20grievances%20of%20people%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20North-East%20and%20Tribal%20areas%20in%20central%20India%20must%20be%20addressed%20for%20ensuring%20peace%20which%20is%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20progress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20now%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20of%20the%20world%20leaving%20China%20behind.%20More%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20is%20below%20the%20age%20of%2025%20years%20and%20more%20than%2065%25%20below%20the%20age%20of%2035.%20However%2C%20this%20population%20dividend%20will%20prove%20ineffective%20if%20adequate%20employment%20opportunities%20are%20not%20available%20in%20the%20country.%20With%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20hovering%20at%20around%207.5%25%2C%20the%20symptoms%20of%20restiveness%20amongst%20youth%20are%20already%20visible.%20Anecdotal%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20people%20involved%20in%20rioting%20and%20vigilantism%20are%20mostly%20unemployed%20youth.%20Unemployment%20therefore%20has%20to%20be%20addressed%20urgently%20by%20strengthening%20the%20manufacturing%20as%20well%20as%20service%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwho-is-afraid-of-otherness%5C%22%3EWho%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20Otherness%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20reason%20often%20cited%20for%20unemployment%20or%20rather%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20employment%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20adequately%20skilled%20man%20power.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20standards%20of%20education%20have%20diluted%20drastically%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20There%20is%20no%20quality%20check%20on%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20resource%20persons%20employed%20in%20the%20educational%20institutions%20which%20have%20mushroomed%20haphazardly%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20We%20are%20therefore%20churning%20out%20under%20qualified%20engineers%2C%20doctors%20and%20MBAs%20from%20establishments%20housed%20in%20one%20or%20two%20rooms%20facility%20without%20any%20laboratories%20or%20other%20essential%20infrastructure.%20These%20establishments%20do%20not%20meet%20the%20stringent%20requirements%20of%20industry%20yet%20manage%20to%20obtain%20approval%20%E2%80%93%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20obtained%20through%20underhand%20means.%20Such%20people%20are%20thus%20compelled%20to%20take%20up%20jobs%20which%20are%20way%20below%20their%20%E2%80%9Cqualification%20on%20paper%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20dissatisfaction.%20Educational%20institutions%20must%20therefore%20be%20subjected%20to%20strict%20quality%20control%20in%20terms%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20resource%20persons%20and%20quality%20and%20content%20of%20education%20imparted.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20must%20also%20focus%20on%20improving%20primary%20education%20in%20far%20flung%20remote%20areas%20and%20villages.%20The%20government%20schools%20in%20villages%20are%20the%20most%20neglected.%20It%20is%20utopian%20to%20expect%20such%20schools%20to%20have%20any%20other%20facility%20essential%20for%20all-round%20personality%20development%20of%20a%20child.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20area%20where%20India%20needs%20to%20focus%20is%20the%20health%20infrastructure.%20While%20we%20are%20focusing%20on%20creating%20tertiary%20level%20facilities%20like%20AIIMS%20in%20big%20cities%2C%20we%20are%20not%20creating%20adequate%20primary%20and%20secondary%20level%20facilities%20in%20villages%2C%20and%20small%20cities%2C%20leading%20to%20overcrowding%20in%20the%20city%20hospitals.%20Only%20a%20healthy%20population%20can%20gainfully%20contribute%20to%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country%20and%20expansion%20of%20our%20economy.%20The%20Primary%20health%20centres%20in%20villages%20must%20be%20strengthened.%20All%20those%20graduating%20from%20medical%20colleges%20must%20be%20compelled%20to%20initially%20work%20in%20rural%20areas%20at%20least%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%20Adequate%20trained%20staff%20and%20medicines%20must%20also%20be%20made%20available%20in%20these%20primary%20health%20centres.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20but%20not%20the%20least%2C%20the%20government%20must%20provide%20a%20humane%20and%20responsive%20administration%20which%20treats%20the%20citizen%20as%20priority.%20It%20is%20often%20seen%20that%20the%20general%20public%20keeps%20running%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20for%20redressal%20of%20even%20minor%20grievances.%20Most%20of%20the%20government%20functionaries%20and%20even%20elected%20representatives%20do%20not%20treat%20common%20public%20with%20empathy.%20Many%20bureaucrats%20resort%20to%20bribe%20taking%20even%20for%20doing%20something%20which%20is%20the%20right%20of%20the%20individual.%20Remote%20villages%20are%20hardly%20ever%20visited%20by%20bureaucrats%20and%20such%20places%20never%20ever%20get%20to%20see%20the%20face%20of%20a%20government%20authority.%20The%20elected%20representatives%20too%20do%20not%20visit%20their%20constituencies%20regularly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpolice-uniform-modi%5C%22%3EReform%2C%20Not%20Uniform%3A%20Why%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Plan%20for%20the%20Police%20in%20India%20is%20Totally%20Off%20the%20Mark%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20neglect%20leads%20to%20dissatisfaction%20and%20is%20cause%20of%20simmering%20unrest%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20avoidable%20agitations.%20Part%20of%20the%20problem%20lies%20in%20the%20selection%20process%20of%20the%20leaders%20heading%20the%20bureaucracy.%20Selected%20through%20a%20testing%20process%20which%20focusses%20mainly%20on%20rote%20memory%2C%20they%20undergo%20motions%20of%20a%20training%20process%20which%20encourages%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20equip%20them%20to%20interpret%20the%20laws%20of%20land%20with%20empathy%2C%20leading%20to%20plethora%20of%20litigation%20where%20the%20government%20is%20either%20a%20litigant%20or%20a%20respondent.%20Not%20that%20litigation%20for%20a%20common%20man%20is%20easy.%20The%20courts%20take%20years%20to%20decide%20a%20case.%20Even%20matters%20like%20granting%20of%20bail%20are%20decided%20after%20lengthy%20arguments%20and%20several%20postponements.%20The%20lower%20courts%20in%20many%20cases%20are%20happy%20abdicating%20their%20responsibility%20by%20passing%20ambiguous%20orders.%20Besides%20the%20unduly%20long%20time%20taken%2C%20litigation%20is%20very%20costly%20which%20a%20regualr%20person%20cannot%20afford%20especially%20in%20the%20High%20courts%20and%20Supreme%20Court.%20Both%20bureaucracy%20and%20judicial%20systems%20are%20in%20urgent%20need%20of%20reforms%20if%20the%20stated%20aim%20of%20government%20is%20to%20be%20achieved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20July%205%20renamed%20%E2%80%9CAmrit%20Kal%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9CKartavya%20Kal%E2%80%9D%20i.e.%20the%20era%20of%20%E2%80%98duty%E2%80%99%2C%20imploring%20the%20public%20to%20perform%20their%20duties%20diligently%20in%20order%20to%20make%20India%20an%20advanced%20country%20during%20the%20period%20leading%20to%202047.%20The%20emphasis%20thus%20has%20been%20placed%20on%20performance%20of%20duties%20as%20the%20first%20priority.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20the%20nation%20cannot%20progress%20without%20every%20citizen%20performing%20their%20duty%20towards%20nation%20building%20diligently.%20However%2C%20reforms%20and%20course%20correction%20suggested%20above%20must%20also%20be%20implemented%20by%20the%20government%20to%20realise%20the%20dream%20of%20India%20becoming%20a%20truly%20progressive%20and%20prosperous%20nation.%20Our%20leaders%20must%20display%20the%20sagacity%20to%20address%20the%20fault%20lines%20and%20work%20with%20single%20minded%20devotion%20to%20achieve%20that%20aim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESanjiv%20Krishan%20Sood%20retired%20as%20additional%20director%20general%2C%20Border%20Security%20Force.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694955645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjust-announcing-good-intentions-wont-lead-india-into-amrit-kaal%22%2C%22summa