20Anupa%20chose%20to%20keep%20the%20originality%20of%20the%20house%20is%20with%20the%20roof%20rafters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20house%20was%20built%20using%20wooden%20rafters%20and%20most%20of%20the%20people%20advised%20us%20to%20change%20it%20to%20steel.%20However%2C%20on%20inspection%2C%20I%20found%20that%20the%20roof%20was%20stronger%20than%20ever.%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20against%20all%20that%20advice%20and%20kept%20the%20original%20rafters%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20Today%2C%20the%20wooden%20rafters%20give%20the%20house%20a%20rustic%20and%20more%20traditional%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChampioning%20sustainability%20during%20renovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnuja%20further%20shares%20that%20to%20keep%20the%20house%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318502%2Fgujarat-eco-friendly-home-stays-cool-without-air-conditioners-sustainable-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20cool%20during%20harsh%20summers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20made%20two%20water%20bodies%20on%20the%20northern%20side%20of%20the%20house%20to%20help%20cool%20the%20wind%20that%20enters%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20house%20more%20sustainable%2C%20Anupa%20also%20added%20water%20gutters%20on%20the%20roof%20to%20use%20the%20rainwater.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20from%20the%20gutters%20flows%20into%20the%20two%20ponds%20that%20we%20have%2C%20and%20we%20also%20store%20it%20to%20use%20the%20water%20for%20landscaping%20the%20house.%20Although%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20the%20gutters%2C%20I%20wanted%20the%20house%20to%20be%20as%20sustainable%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857.jpg%5C%22%20wid