20substances%20used%20in%20the%20renovation%20of%20the%20house%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328878%2Fcouple-builds-saroga-woods-carbon-friendly-solar-powered-sustainable-homestay-in-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycled%20and%20upcycled%20materials.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CUpcycling%20and%20recycling%20the%20materials%20while%20refurbishing%20the%20house%20helped%20us%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Most%20of%20our%20family%20and%20friends%20speculated%20the%20cost%20to%20be%20around%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20when%20we%20started%20and%20advised%20us%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20house%20instead.%20However%2C%20I%20told%20them%20I%20will%20bring%20down%20the%20cost%20simply%20by%20reusing%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20precisely%20what%20Anupa%20did%2C%20and%20she%20was%20able%20to%20renovate%20the%20house%20fully%20for%20just%20Rs%2030%20lakh%2C%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCp-DrilPmyl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCp-DrilPmyl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3