%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hamlet%2C%20which%20was%20once%20occupied%20by%20Girdhar%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20is%20now%20converted%20into%20the%20improved%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256646%2Futtarakhand-kumaon-ecofriendly-travel-destination-sustainable-homestay-organic-farm-solar-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidential%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20farm.%20The%20Barad%20brothers%20say%20that%20all%20they%20did%20was%20extend%20the%20bedrooms%2C%20add%20a%2070-ft%20verandah%20and%20make%20harmonious%20cosmetic%20changes%20to%20marry%20the%20inside%20and%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20bungalow%20in%20the%202022%20monsoons.%20Among%20delays%20in%20receiving%20material%20due%20to%20the%20rains%2C%20we%20also%20experienced%20frequent%20electricity%20cuts.%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20overseeing%20the%20site%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nishit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20three%20years%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329447%2Fdevra-homestay-in-udaipur-barren-land-to-heritage-property%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erigorous%20effort%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20toil%2C%20it%20was%20worth%20it.%20Though%20accustomed%20to%20luxuries%20such%20as%20air%20conditioners%20and%20geysers%20back%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20brothers%20shared%20how%20they%20managed%20very%20well%20without%20these%20and%20had%20a%20good%20time%20all%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20wanted%20to%20share%20this%20experience%20with%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Nishit%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CEspecially%20with%20our%20friends%20who%20told%20us%20how%20they%20were%20frustrated%20with%20the%20urban%20life%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20connection%20with%20nature%2C%20and%20how%20their%20kids%20were%20missing%20out%20on%20the%20joys%20of%2