EBetween%202004%20and%202006%2C%20there%20was%20a%20concerning%20increase%20in%20farmer%20suicides%2C%20particularly%20in%20Maharashtra.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ENCRB%3C%2Fem%3E%20data%2C%20in%202006%2C%2017%2C060%20farmers%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20the%20country%2C%20of%20which%201%2C427%20were%20from%20Maharashtra.%20And%201%2C065%20of%20these%20deaths%20occurred%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20cotton%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20deeply%20disturbed%20Sharmila%20Jain%20Oswal%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Canada%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20earning%20good%20money%2C%20I%20was%20not%20on%20my%20own%20soil.%20I%20yearned%20to%20return%20and%20support%20the%20farmers%2C%20contributing%20to%20my%20nation%E2%80%99s%20nutritional%20security.%20Growing%20up%20in%20a%20village%2C%20I%20had%20seen%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307428%2Fhow-did-pathankot-record-just-one-farm-fire-chief-agricultural-officer-dr-amrik-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplight%20of%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20knew%20their%20problems%20firsthand.%20Sadly%2C%20many%20government%20initiatives%20failed%20to%20reach%20them%2C%20leading%20to%20mounting%20debts%20and%20poor%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2052-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Sharmila%20decided%20to%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20returned%20to%20Pune%20in%202008.%20She%20then%20embarked%20on%20a%20two-year%20survey%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Rajasthan%20to%20understand%20the%20problems%20faced%20by%20farmers%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20she%20established%20an%20NGO%20named%20the%20Green%20Energy%20Foundation%20to%20provide%20solutions%20to%20farmers.%20The%20foundation%20focuses%20on%20the%20revival%20of%20water%20sources%20and%20implementing%20smart%20farming%20techniques%2C%20while%20empowering