0a%20ride%20across%20town.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20change%20gears.%20But%20I%20learnt%20these%20things.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20month%20after%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F74957%2Fmohit-kapoor-solo-cyclist-traveller-southeast-asia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eriding%20her%20precious%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20day%2C%20Renu%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20MTB%2060%20km%20(mountain%20biking)%20challenge%20%E2%80%9Cpurely%20for%20fun%E2%80%9D%20and%20ended%20up%20coming%20second!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20saying%20%E2%80%98Look!%20She%20just%20started%20cycling%20a%20month%20back%20and%20now%20she%20is%20doing%20all%20these%20events.%E2%80%99%20But%20I%20was%20just%20having%20fun.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20duo%20met%20at%20LEL%2C%20Gareema%20recounts%20feeling%20in%20awe%20not%20just%20of%20Renu%E2%80%99s%20cycling%20prowess%20but%20also%20of%20the%20force%20of%20nature%20that%20she%20was.%20The%20duo%20bonded%20over%20the%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%20that%20cycling%20had%20been%20for%20the%20both%20of%20them.%20While%20for%20Renu%20it%20had%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20proving%20that%20age%20is%20just%20a%20number%2C%20for%20Gareema%20it%20was%20about%20finding%20her%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG-20230908-WA0001-1694174552.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Renu%20Singhi%20is%20often%20called%20the%20'grandmother%20who%20cycles'%20as%20she%20continues%20to%20cycle%20at%20the%20age%20of%2058%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG-20230908-WA0001-1694174552.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media